var book = {
	"name": "Acts",
	"numChapters": 28,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The first account I composed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26925A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26925A\"></sup>Theophilus, about all that Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26925B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26925B\"></sup>began to do and teach,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>until the day when He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26926C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26926C\"></sup>was taken up <i>to heaven</i>, after He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26926D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26926D\"></sup>had by the Holy Spirit given orders to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26926E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26926E\"></sup>the apostles whom He had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26926F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26926F\"></sup>chosen.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>To these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26927G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26927G\"></sup>He also presented Himself alive after His suffering, by many convincing proofs, appearing to them over <i>a period of</i> forty days and speaking of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26927H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26927H\"></sup>the things concerning the kingdom of God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Gathering them together, He commanded them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26928I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26928I\"></sup>not to leave Jerusalem, but to wait for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26928J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26928J\"></sup>what the Father had promised, <span class=\"woj\">“Which,”</span> <i>He said</i>, <span class=\"woj\">“you heard of from Me;</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26929K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26929K\"></sup>John baptized with water, but you will be baptized with the Holy Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26929L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26929L\"></sup>not many days from now.”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So when they had come together, they were asking Him, saying, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26930M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26930M\"></sup>is it at this time You are restoring the kingdom to Israel?”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“It is not for you to know times or epochs which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26931N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26931N\"></sup>the Father has fixed by His own authority;</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>but you will receive power <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26932O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26932O\"></sup>when the Holy Spirit has come upon you; and you shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26932P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26932P\"></sup>My witnesses both in Jerusalem, and in all Judea and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26932Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26932Q\"></sup>Samaria, and even to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26932R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26932R\"></sup>the remotest part of the earth.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And after He had said these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26933S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26933S\"></sup>He was lifted up while they were looking on, and a cloud received Him out of their sight.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And as they were gazing intently into the sky while He was going, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26934T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26934T\"></sup>two men in white clothing stood beside them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They also said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26935U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26935U\"></sup>Men of Galilee, why do you stand looking into the sky? This Jesus, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26935V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26935V\"></sup>has been taken up from you into heaven, will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26935W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26935W\"></sup>come in just the same way as you have watched Him go into heaven.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26936X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26936X\"></sup>returned to Jerusalem from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26936Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26936Y\"></sup>mount called Olivet, which is near Jerusalem, a Sabbath day’s journey away.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When they had entered <i>the city</i>, they went up to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26937Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26937Z\"></sup>the upper room where they were staying; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26937AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26937AA\"></sup>that is, Peter and John and James and Andrew, Philip and Thomas, Bartholomew and Matthew, James <i>the son</i> of Alphaeus, and Simon the Zealot, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26937AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26937AB\"></sup>Judas <i>the</i> <i>son</i> of James.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>These all with one mind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26938AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26938AC\"></sup>were continually devoting themselves to prayer, along with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26938AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26938AD\"></sup><i>the</i> women, and Mary the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26938AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26938AE\"></sup>mother of Jesus, and with His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26938AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26938AF\"></sup>brothers.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>At this time Peter stood up in the midst of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26939AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26939AG\"></sup>the brethren (a gathering of about one hundred and twenty persons was there together), and said,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Brethren, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26940AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26940AH\"></sup>the Scripture had to be fulfilled, which the Holy Spirit foretold by the mouth of David concerning Judas, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26940AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26940AI\"></sup>who became a guide to those who arrested Jesus.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26941AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26941AJ\"></sup>counted among us and received his share in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26941AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26941AK\"></sup>this ministry.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>(Now this man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26942AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26942AL\"></sup>acquired a field with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26942AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26942AM\"></sup>the price of his wickedness, and falling headlong, he burst open in the middle and all his intestines gushed out.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And it became known to all who were living in Jerusalem; so that in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26943AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26943AN\"></sup>their own language that field was called Hakeldama, that is, Field of Blood.)",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“For it is written in the book of Psalms,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26944AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26944AO\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Let his homestead be made desolate</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And let no one dwell in it</span>’;and,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26944AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26944AP\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Let another man take his</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">office</span>.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore it is necessary that of the men who have accompanied us all the time that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26945AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26945AQ\"></sup>the Lord Jesus went in and out among us—",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26946AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26946AR\"></sup>beginning with the baptism of John until the day that He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26946AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26946AS\"></sup>was taken up from us—one of these <i>must</i> become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26946AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26946AT\"></sup>witness with us of His resurrection.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>So they put forward two men, Joseph called Barsabbas (who was also called Justus), and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26947AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26947AU\"></sup>Matthias.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26948AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26948AV\"></sup>prayed and said, “You, Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26948AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26948AW\"></sup>who know the hearts of all men, show which one of these two You have chosen",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>to occupy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26949AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26949AX\"></sup>this ministry and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26949AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26949AY\"></sup>apostleship from which Judas turned aside to go to his own place.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26950AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26950AZ\"></sup>drew lots for them, and the lot fell to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26950BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26950BA\"></sup>Matthias; and he was added to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26950BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26950BB\"></sup>the eleven apostles."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26951A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26951A\"></sup>the day of Pentecost had come, they were all together in one place.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And suddenly there came from heaven a noise like a violent rushing wind, and it filled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26952B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26952B\"></sup>the whole house where they were sitting.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And there appeared to them tongues as of fire distributing themselves, and they rested on each one of them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And they were all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26954C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26954C\"></sup>filled with the Holy Spirit and began to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26954D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26954D\"></sup>speak with other tongues, as the Spirit was giving them utterance.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now there were Jews living in Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26955E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26955E\"></sup>devout men from every nation under heaven.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26956F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26956F\"></sup>this sound occurred, the crowd came together, and were bewildered because each one of them was hearing them speak in his own language.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26957G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26957G\"></sup>They were amazed and astonished, saying, “Why, are not all these who are speaking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26957H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26957H\"></sup>Galileans?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And how is it that we each hear <i>them</i> in our own language to which we were born?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Parthians and Medes and Elamites, and residents of Mesopotamia, Judea and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26959I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26959I\"></sup>Cappadocia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26959J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26959J\"></sup>Pontus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26959K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26959K\"></sup>Asia,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26960L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26960L\"></sup>Phrygia and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26960M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26960M\"></sup>Pamphylia, Egypt and the districts of Libya around <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26960N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26960N\"></sup>Cyrene, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26960O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26960O\"></sup>visitors from Rome, both Jews and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26960P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26960P\"></sup>proselytes,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Cretans and Arabs—we hear them in our <i>own</i> tongues speaking of the mighty deeds of God.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26962Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26962Q\"></sup>they all continued in amazement and great perplexity, saying to one another, “What does this mean?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But others were mocking and saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26963R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26963R\"></sup>They are full of sweet wine.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But Peter, taking his stand with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26964S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26964S\"></sup>the eleven, raised his voice and declared to them: “Men of Judea and all you who live in Jerusalem, let this be known to you and give heed to my words.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For these men are not drunk, as you suppose, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26965T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26965T\"></sup>for it is <i>only</i> the third hour of the day;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>but this is what was spoken of through the prophet Joel:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26967U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26967U\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And it shall be in the last days</span>,’ God says,‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">That I will pour forth of My Spirit on all</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">mankind</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And your sons and your daughters shall prophesy</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And your young men shall see visions</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And your old men shall dream dreams</span>;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Even on My bondslaves, both men and women</span>,I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will in those days pour forth of My Spirit</span>And they shall prophesy.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And I will grant wonders in the sky above</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And signs on the earth below</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Blood, and fire, and vapor of smoke</span>.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The sun will be turned into darkness</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And the moon into blood</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Before the great and glorious day of the Lord shall come</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And it shall be that</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26971V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26971V\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">everyone who calls on the name of the Lord will be saved</span>.’",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Men of Israel, listen to these words: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26972W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26972W\"></sup>Jesus the Nazarene, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26972X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26972X\"></sup>a man attested to you by God with miracles and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26972Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26972Y\"></sup>wonders and signs which God performed through Him in your midst, just as you yourselves know—",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>this <i>Man</i>, delivered over by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26973Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26973Z\"></sup>predetermined plan and foreknowledge of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26973AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26973AA\"></sup>you nailed to a cross by the hands of godless men and put <i>Him</i> to death.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26974AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26974AB\"></sup>God raised Him up again, putting an end to the agony of death, since it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26974AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26974AC\"></sup>was impossible for Him to be held in its power.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For David says of Him,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26975AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26975AD\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">saw the Lord always in my presence</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For He is at my right hand, so that I will not be shaken</span>.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Therefore my heart was glad and my tongue exulted</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Moreover my flesh also will live in hope</span>;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Because You will not abandon my soul to</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26977AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26977AE\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Hades</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26977AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26977AF\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Nor</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">allow Your</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Holy One to</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">undergo decay</span>.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You have made known to me the ways of life</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You will make me full of gladness with Your presence</span>.’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Brethren, I may confidently say to you regarding the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26979AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26979AG\"></sup>patriarch David that he both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26979AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26979AH\"></sup>died and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26979AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26979AI\"></sup>was buried, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26979AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26979AJ\"></sup>his tomb is with us to this day.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And so, because he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26980AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26980AK\"></sup>a prophet and knew that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26980AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26980AL\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God had sworn to him with an oath to seat</span> <i>one</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">of his descendants on his throne</span>,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>he looked ahead and spoke of the resurrection of the Christ, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26981AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26981AM\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He was neither abandoned to Hades, nor did</span> His flesh <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">suffer decay</span>.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>This Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26982AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26982AN\"></sup>God raised up again, to which we are all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26982AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26982AO\"></sup>witnesses.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Therefore having been exalted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26983AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26983AP\"></sup>to the right hand of God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26983AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26983AQ\"></sup>having received from the Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26983AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26983AR\"></sup>the promise of the Holy Spirit, He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26983AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26983AS\"></sup>poured forth this which you both see and hear.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For it was not David who ascended into heaven, but he himself says:‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26984AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26984AT\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The Lord said to my Lord</span>,“<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Sit at My right hand</span>,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Until I make Your enemies a footstool for Your feet</span>.”’",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Therefore let all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26986AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26986AU\"></sup>house of Israel know for certain that God has made Him both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26986AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26986AV\"></sup>Lord and Christ—this Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26986AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26986AW\"></sup>whom you crucified.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Now when they heard <i>this</i>, they were pierced to the heart, and said to Peter and the rest of the apostles, “Brethren, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26987AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26987AX\"></sup>what shall we do?”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Peter <i>said</i> to them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26988AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26988AY\"></sup>Repent, and each of you be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26988AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26988AZ\"></sup>baptized in the name of Jesus Christ for the forgiveness of your sins; and you will receive the gift of the Holy Spirit.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26989BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26989BA\"></sup>the promise is for you and your children and for all who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26989BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26989BB\"></sup>far off, as many as the Lord our God will call to Himself.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And with many other words he solemnly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26990BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26990BC\"></sup>testified and kept on exhorting them, saying, “Be saved from this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26990BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26990BD\"></sup>perverse generation!”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>So then, those who had received his word were baptized; and that day there were added about three thousand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26991BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26991BE\"></sup>souls.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>They were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26992BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26992BF\"></sup>continually devoting themselves to the apostles’ teaching and to fellowship, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26992BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26992BG\"></sup>the breaking of bread and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26992BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26992BH\"></sup>to prayer.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Everyone kept feeling a sense of awe; and many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26993BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26993BI\"></sup>wonders and signs were taking place through the apostles.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And all those who had believed were together and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26994BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26994BJ\"></sup>had all things in common;",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26995BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26995BK\"></sup><i>began</i> selling their property and possessions and were sharing them with all, as anyone might have need.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26996BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26996BL\"></sup>Day by day continuing with one mind in the temple, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26996BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26996BM\"></sup>breaking bread from house to house, they were taking their meals together with gladness and sincerity of heart,",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>praising God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26997BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26997BN\"></sup>having favor with all the people. And the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26997BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26997BO\"></sup>was adding to their number day by day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26997BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26997BP\"></sup>those who were being saved."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26998A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26998A\"></sup>Peter and John were going up to the temple at the ninth <i>hour</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26998B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26998B\"></sup>the hour of prayer.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26999C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26999C\"></sup>a man who had been lame from his mother’s womb was being carried along, whom they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26999D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26999D\"></sup>used to set down every day at the gate of the temple which is called Beautiful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26999E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26999E\"></sup>in order to beg alms of those who were entering the temple.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When he saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27000F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27000F\"></sup>Peter and John about to go into the temple, he <i>began</i> asking to receive alms.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But Peter, along with John, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27001G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27001G\"></sup>fixed his gaze on him and said, “Look at us!”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And he <i>began</i> to give them his attention, expecting to receive something from them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But Peter said, “I do not possess silver and gold, but what I do have I give to you: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27003H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27003H\"></sup>In the name of Jesus Christ the Nazarene—walk!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And seizing him by the right hand, he raised him up; and immediately his feet and his ankles were strengthened.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27005I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27005I\"></sup>With a leap he stood upright and <i>began</i> to walk; and he entered the temple with them, walking and leaping and praising God.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27006J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27006J\"></sup>all the people saw him walking and praising God;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and they were taking note of him as being the one who used to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27007K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27007K\"></sup>sit at the Beautiful Gate of the temple to <i>beg</i> alms, and they were filled with wonder and amazement at what had happened to him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>While he was clinging to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27008L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27008L\"></sup>Peter and John, all the people ran together to them at the so-called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27008M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27008M\"></sup>portico of Solomon, full of amazement.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But when Peter saw <i>this</i>, he replied to the people, “Men of Israel, why are you amazed at this, or why do you gaze at us, as if by our own power or piety we had made him walk?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27010N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27010N\"></sup>The God of Abraham, Isaac and Jacob, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27010O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27010O\"></sup>the God of our fathers, has glorified His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27010P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27010P\"></sup>servant Jesus, <i>the one</i> whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27010Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27010Q\"></sup>you delivered and disowned in the presence of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27010R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27010R\"></sup>Pilate, when he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27010S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27010S\"></sup>decided to release Him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But you disowned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27011T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27011T\"></sup>the Holy and Righteous One and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27011U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27011U\"></sup>asked for a murderer to be granted to you,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>but put to death the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27012V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27012V\"></sup>Prince of life, <i>the one</i> whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27012W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27012W\"></sup>God raised from the dead, <i>a fact</i> to which we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27012X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27012X\"></sup>witnesses.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And on the basis of faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27013Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27013Y\"></sup>in His name, <i>it is</i> the name of Jesus which has strengthened this man whom you see and know; and the faith which <i>comes</i> through Him has given him this perfect health in the presence of you all.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“And now, brethren, I know that you acted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27014Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27014Z\"></sup>in ignorance, just as your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27014AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27014AA\"></sup>rulers did also.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But the things which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27015AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27015AB\"></sup>God announced beforehand by the mouth of all the prophets, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27015AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27015AC\"></sup>that His Christ would suffer, He has thus fulfilled.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27016AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27016AD\"></sup>repent and return, so that your sins may be wiped away, in order that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27016AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27016AE\"></sup>times of refreshing may come from the presence of the Lord;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and that He may send Jesus, the Christ appointed for you,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27018AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27018AF\"></sup>whom heaven must receive until <i>the</i> period of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27018AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27018AG\"></sup>restoration of all things about which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27018AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27018AH\"></sup>God spoke by the mouth of His holy prophets from ancient time.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Moses said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27019AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27019AI\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The Lord God will raise up for you a prophet</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">like me from your brethren; to Him you shall give heed</span> to everything He says to you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27020AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27020AJ\"></sup>And it will be that every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27020AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27020AK\"></sup>soul that does not heed that prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27020AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27020AL\"></sup>shall be utterly destroyed from among the people.’",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And likewise, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27021AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27021AM\"></sup>all the prophets who have spoken, from Samuel and <i>his</i> successors onward, also announced these days.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>It is you who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27022AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27022AN\"></sup>the sons of the prophets and of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27022AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27022AO\"></sup>covenant which God made with your fathers, saying to Abraham, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27022AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27022AP\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And in your seed all the families of the earth shall be blessed</span>.’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27023AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27023AQ\"></sup>first, God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27023AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27023AR\"></sup>raised up His Servant and sent Him to bless you by turning every one <i>of you</i> from your wicked ways.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>As they were speaking to the people, the priests and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27024A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27024A\"></sup>the captain of the temple <i>guard</i> and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27024B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27024B\"></sup>the Sadducees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27024C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27024C\"></sup>came up to them,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>being greatly disturbed because they were teaching the people and proclaiming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27025D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27025D\"></sup>in Jesus the resurrection from the dead.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And they laid hands on them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27026E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27026E\"></sup>put them in jail until the next day, for it was already evening.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But many of those who had heard the message believed; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27027F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27027F\"></sup>the number of the men came to be about five thousand.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>On the next day, their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27028G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27028G\"></sup>rulers and elders and scribes were gathered together in Jerusalem;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27029H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27029H\"></sup>Annas the high priest <i>was there</i>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27029I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27029I\"></sup>Caiaphas and John and Alexander, and all who were of high-priestly descent.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When they had placed them in the center, they <i>began to</i> inquire, “By what power, or in what name, have you done this?”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then Peter, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27031J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27031J\"></sup>filled with the Holy Spirit, said to them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27031K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27031K\"></sup>Rulers and elders of the people,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>if we are on trial today for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27032L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27032L\"></sup>a benefit done to a sick man, as to how this man has been made well,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>let it be known to all of you and to all the people of Israel, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27033M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27033M\"></sup>by the name of Jesus Christ the Nazarene, whom you crucified, whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27033N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27033N\"></sup>God raised from the dead—by this <i>name</i> this man stands here before you in good health.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27034O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27034O\"></sup>He is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27034P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27034P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">stone which was</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27034Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27034Q\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">rejected</span> by you, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the builders</span>, <i>but</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">which became the chief corner</span> <i>stone</i>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And there is salvation in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27035R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27035R\"></sup>no one else; for there is no other name under heaven that has been given among men by which we must be saved.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now as they observed the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27036S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27036S\"></sup>confidence of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27036T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27036T\"></sup>Peter and John and understood that they were uneducated and untrained men, they were amazed, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27036U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27036U\"></sup><i>began</i> to recognize them as having been with Jesus.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And seeing the man who had been healed standing with them, they had nothing to say in reply.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But when they had ordered them to leave the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27038V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27038V\"></sup>Council, they <i>began</i> to confer with one another,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27039W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27039W\"></sup>What shall we do with these men? For the fact that a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27039X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27039X\"></sup>noteworthy miracle has taken place through them is apparent to all who live in Jerusalem, and we cannot deny it.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But so that it will not spread any further among the people, let us warn them to speak no longer to any man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27040Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27040Y\"></sup>in this name.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And when they had summoned them, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27041Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27041Z\"></sup>commanded them not to speak or teach at all in the name of Jesus.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27042AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27042AA\"></sup>Peter and John answered and said to them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27042AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27042AB\"></sup>Whether it is right in the sight of God to give heed to you rather than to God, you be the judge;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27043AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27043AC\"></sup>we cannot stop speaking about what we have seen and heard.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>When they had threatened them further, they let them go (finding no basis on which to punish them) <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27044AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27044AD\"></sup>on account of the people, because they were all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27044AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27044AE\"></sup>glorifying God for what had happened;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>for the man was more than forty years old on whom this miracle of healing had been performed.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When they had been released, they went to their own <i>companions</i> and reported all that the chief priests and the elders had said to them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And when they heard <i>this</i>, they lifted their voices to God with one accord and said, “O Lord, it is You who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27047AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27047AF\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">made the heaven and the earth and the sea, and all that is in them</span>,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27048AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27048AG\"></sup>by the Holy Spirit, <i>through</i> the mouth of our father David Your servant, said,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27048AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27048AH\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Why did the</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Gentiles rage</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And the peoples devise futile things</span>?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27049AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27049AI\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The kings of the earth</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">took their stand</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And the rulers were gathered together</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Against the Lord and against His</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27049AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27049AJ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Christ</span>.’",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For truly in this city there were gathered together against Your holy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27050AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27050AK\"></sup>servant Jesus, whom You anointed, both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27050AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27050AL\"></sup>Herod and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27050AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27050AM\"></sup>Pontius Pilate, along with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27050AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27050AN\"></sup>the Gentiles and the peoples of Israel,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>to do whatever Your hand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27051AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27051AO\"></sup>Your purpose predestined to occur.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And now, Lord, take note of their threats, and grant that Your bond-servants may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27052AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27052AP\"></sup>speak Your word with all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27052AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27052AQ\"></sup>confidence,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>while You extend Your hand to heal, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27053AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27053AR\"></sup>signs and wonders take place through the name of Your holy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27053AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27053AS\"></sup>servant Jesus.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And when they had prayed, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27054AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27054AT\"></sup>place where they had gathered together was shaken, and they were all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27054AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27054AU\"></sup>filled with the Holy Spirit and <i>began</i> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27054AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27054AV\"></sup>speak the word of God with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27054AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27054AW\"></sup>boldness.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And the congregation of those who believed were of one heart and soul; and not one <i>of them</i> claimed that anything belonging to him was his own, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27055AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27055AX\"></sup>all things were common property to them.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27056AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27056AY\"></sup>with great power the apostles were giving <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27056AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27056AZ\"></sup>testimony to the resurrection of the Lord Jesus, and abundant grace was upon them all.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For there was not a needy person among them, for all who were owners of land or houses <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27057BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27057BA\"></sup>would sell them and bring the proceeds of the sales",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27058BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27058BB\"></sup>lay them at the apostles’ feet, and they would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27058BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27058BC\"></sup>distributed to each as any had need.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Now Joseph, a Levite of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27059BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27059BD\"></sup>Cyprian birth, who was also called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27059BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27059BE\"></sup>Barnabas by the apostles (which translated means Son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27059BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27059BF\"></sup>Encouragement),",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>and who owned a tract of land, sold it and brought the money and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27060BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27060BG\"></sup>laid it at the apostles’ feet."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>But a man named Ananias, with his wife Sapphira, sold a piece of property,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27062A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27062A\"></sup>kept back <i>some</i> of the price for himself, with his wife’s full knowledge, and bringing a portion of it, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27062B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27062B\"></sup>laid it at the apostles’ feet.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But Peter said, “Ananias, why has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27063C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27063C\"></sup>Satan filled your heart to lie <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27063D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27063D\"></sup>to the Holy Spirit and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27063E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27063E\"></sup>keep back <i>some</i> of the price of the land?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>While it remained <i>unsold</i>, did it not remain your own? And after it was sold, was it not under your control? Why is it that you have conceived this deed in your heart? You have not lied to men but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27064F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27064F\"></sup>to God.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And as he heard these words, Ananias <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27065G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27065G\"></sup>fell down and breathed his last; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27065H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27065H\"></sup>great fear came over all who heard of it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The young men got up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27066I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27066I\"></sup>covered him up, and after carrying him out, they buried him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now there elapsed an interval of about three hours, and his wife came in, not knowing what had happened.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And Peter responded to her, “Tell me whether you sold the land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27068J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27068J\"></sup>for such and such a price?” And she said, “Yes, that was the price.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then Peter <i>said</i> to her, “Why is it that you have agreed together to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27069K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27069K\"></sup>put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27069L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27069L\"></sup>the Spirit of the Lord to the test? Behold, the feet of those who have buried your husband are at the door, and they will carry you out <i>as well</i>.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And immediately she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27070M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27070M\"></sup>fell at his feet and breathed her last, and the young men came in and found her dead, and they carried her out and buried her beside her husband.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27071N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27071N\"></sup>great fear came over the whole church, and over all who heard of these things.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>At the hands of the apostles many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27072O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27072O\"></sup>signs and wonders were taking place among the people; and they were all with one accord in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27072P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27072P\"></sup>Solomon’s portico.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But none of the rest dared to associate with them; however, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27073Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27073Q\"></sup>the people held them in high esteem.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And all the more <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27074R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27074R\"></sup>believers in the Lord, multitudes of men and women, were constantly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27074S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27074S\"></sup>added to <i>their number</i>,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>to such an extent that they even carried the sick out into the streets and laid them on cots and pallets, so that when Peter came by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27075T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27075T\"></sup>at least his shadow might fall on any one of them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Also the people from the cities in the vicinity of Jerusalem were coming together, bringing people who were sick or afflicted with unclean spirits, and they were all being healed.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But the high priest rose up, along with all his associates (that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27077U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27077U\"></sup>the sect of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27077V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27077V\"></sup>the Sadducees), and they were filled with jealousy.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They laid hands on the apostles and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27078W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27078W\"></sup>put them in a public jail.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But during the night <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27079X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27079X\"></sup>an angel of the Lord opened the gates of the prison, and taking them out he said,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Go, stand and speak to the people in the temple <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27080Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27080Y\"></sup>the whole message of this Life.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Upon hearing <i>this</i>, they entered into the temple <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27081Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27081Z\"></sup>about daybreak and <i>began</i> to teach.Now when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27081AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27081AA\"></sup>the high priest and his associates came, they called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27081AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27081AB\"></sup>the Council together, even all the Senate of the sons of Israel, and sent <i>orders</i> to the prison house for them to be brought.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27082AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27082AC\"></sup>the officers who came did not find them in the prison; and they returned and reported back,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>saying, “We found the prison house locked quite securely and the guards standing at the doors; but when we had opened up, we found no one inside.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27084AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27084AD\"></sup>the captain of the temple <i>guard</i> and the chief priests heard these words, they were greatly perplexed about them as to what would come of this.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But someone came and reported to them, “The men whom you put in prison are standing in the temple and teaching the people!”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27086AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27086AE\"></sup>the captain went along with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27086AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27086AF\"></sup>the officers and <i>proceeded</i> to bring them <i>back</i> without violence (for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27086AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27086AG\"></sup>they were afraid of the people, that they might be stoned).",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When they had brought them, they stood them before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27087AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27087AH\"></sup>the Council. The high priest questioned them,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>saying, “We gave you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27088AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27088AI\"></sup>strict orders not to continue teaching in this name, and yet, you have filled Jerusalem with your teaching and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27088AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27088AJ\"></sup>intend to bring this man’s blood upon us.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But Peter and the apostles answered, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27089AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27089AK\"></sup>We must obey God rather than men.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27090AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27090AL\"></sup>The God of our fathers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27090AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27090AM\"></sup>raised up Jesus, whom you had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27090AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27090AN\"></sup>put to death by hanging Him on a cross.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27091AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27091AO\"></sup>He is the one whom God exalted to His right hand as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27091AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27091AP\"></sup>Prince and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27091AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27091AQ\"></sup>Savior, to grant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27091AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27091AR\"></sup>repentance to Israel, and forgiveness of sins.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27092AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27092AS\"></sup>witnesses of these things; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27092AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27092AT\"></sup><i>so is</i> the Holy Spirit, whom God has given to those who obey Him.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But when they heard this, they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27093AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27093AU\"></sup>cut to the quick and intended to kill them.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But a Pharisee named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27094AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27094AV\"></sup>Gamaliel, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27094AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27094AW\"></sup>teacher of the Law, respected by all the people, stood up in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27094AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27094AX\"></sup>the Council and gave orders to put the men outside for a short time.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And he said to them, “Men of Israel, take care what you propose to do with these men.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>For some time ago Theudas rose up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27096AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27096AY\"></sup>claiming to be somebody, and a group of about four hundred men joined up with him. But he was killed, and all who followed him were dispersed and came to nothing.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>After this man, Judas of Galilee rose up in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27097AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27097AZ\"></sup>the census and drew away <i>some</i> people after him; he too perished, and all those who followed him were scattered.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>So in the present case, I say to you, stay away from these men and let them alone, for if this plan or action <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27098BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27098BA\"></sup>is of men, it will be overthrown;",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>but if it is of God, you will not be able to overthrow them; or else you may even be found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27099BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27099BB\"></sup>fighting against God.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>They took his advice; and after calling the apostles in, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27100BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27100BC\"></sup>flogged them and ordered them not to speak in the name of Jesus, and <i>then</i> released them.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>So they went on their way from the presence of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27101BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27101BD\"></sup>Council, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27101BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27101BE\"></sup>rejoicing that they had been considered worthy to suffer shame <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27101BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27101BF\"></sup>for <i>His</i> name.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27102BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27102BG\"></sup>And every day, in the temple and from house to house, they kept right on teaching and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27102BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27102BH\"></sup>preaching Jesus <i>as</i> the Christ."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Now at this time while the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27103A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27103A\"></sup>disciples were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27103B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27103B\"></sup>increasing <i>in number</i>, a complaint arose on the part of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27103C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27103C\"></sup>Hellenistic <i>Jews</i> against the <i>native</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27103D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27103D\"></sup>Hebrews, because their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27103E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27103E\"></sup>widows were being overlooked in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27103F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27103F\"></sup>the daily serving <i>of food</i>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So the twelve summoned the congregation of the disciples and said, “It is not desirable for us to neglect the word of God in order to serve tables.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27105G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27105G\"></sup>brethren, select from among you seven men of good reputation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27105H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27105H\"></sup>full of the Spirit and of wisdom, whom we may put in charge of this task.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But we will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27106I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27106I\"></sup>devote ourselves to prayer and to the ministry of the word.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The statement found approval with the whole congregation; and they chose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27107J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27107J\"></sup>Stephen, a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27107K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27107K\"></sup>full of faith and of the Holy Spirit, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27107L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27107L\"></sup>Philip, Prochorus, Nicanor, Timon, Parmenas and Nicolas, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27107M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27107M\"></sup>proselyte from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27107N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27107N\"></sup>Antioch.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And these they brought before the apostles; and after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27108O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27108O\"></sup>praying, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27108P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27108P\"></sup>laid their hands on them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27109Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27109Q\"></sup>The word of God kept on spreading; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27109R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27109R\"></sup>the number of the disciples continued to increase greatly in Jerusalem, and a great many of the priests were becoming obedient to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27109S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27109S\"></sup>the faith.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And Stephen, full of grace and power, was performing great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27110T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27110T\"></sup>wonders and signs among the people.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But some men from what was called the Synagogue of the Freedmen, <i>including</i> both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27111U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27111U\"></sup>Cyrenians and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27111V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27111V\"></sup>Alexandrians, and some from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27111W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27111W\"></sup>Cilicia and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27111X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27111X\"></sup>Asia, rose up and argued with Stephen.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But they were unable to cope with the wisdom and the Spirit with which he was speaking.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then they secretly induced men to say, “We have heard him speak blasphemous words against Moses and <i>against</i> God.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And they stirred up the people, the elders and the scribes, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27114Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27114Y\"></sup>came up to him and dragged him away and brought him before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27114Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27114Z\"></sup>the Council.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They put forward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27115AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27115AA\"></sup>false witnesses who said, “This man incessantly speaks against this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27115AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27115AB\"></sup>holy place and the Law;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>for we have heard him say that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27116AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27116AC\"></sup>this Nazarene, Jesus, will destroy this place and alter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27116AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27116AD\"></sup>the customs which Moses handed down to us.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And fixing their gaze on him, all who were sitting in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27117AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27117AE\"></sup>Council saw his face like the face of an angel."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>The high priest said, “Are these things so?”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he said, “Hear me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27119A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27119A\"></sup>brethren and fathers! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27119B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27119B\"></sup>The God of glory <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27119C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27119C\"></sup>appeared to our father Abraham when he was in Mesopotamia, before he lived in Haran,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and said to him, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27120D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27120D\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Leave your country and your relatives, and come into the land that I will show you</span>.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27121E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27121E\"></sup>Then he left the land of the Chaldeans and settled in Haran. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27121F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27121F\"></sup>From there, after his father died, <i>God</i> had him move to this country in which you are now living.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But He gave him no inheritance in it, not even a foot of ground, and <i>yet</i>, even when he had no child, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27122G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27122G\"></sup>He promised that <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He would give it to him as a possession, and to his descendants after him</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27123H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27123H\"></sup>God spoke to this effect, that his <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">descendants would be aliens in a foreign land, and that they would</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">be enslaved and mistreated for four hundred years</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And whatever nation to which they will be in bondage I Myself will judge</span>,’ said God, ‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">and</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27124I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27124I\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">after that they will come out and</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">serve Me in this place</span>.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27125J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27125J\"></sup>gave him the covenant of circumcision; and so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27125K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27125K\"></sup><i>Abraham</i> became the father of Isaac, and circumcised him on the eighth day; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27125L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27125L\"></sup>Isaac <i>became the father of</i> Jacob, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27125M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27125M\"></sup>Jacob <i>of</i> the twelve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27125N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27125N\"></sup>patriarchs.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The patriarchs <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27126O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27126O\"></sup>became jealous of Joseph and sold him into Egypt. <i>Yet</i> God was with him,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and rescued him from all his afflictions, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27127P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27127P\"></sup>granted him favor and wisdom in the sight of Pharaoh, king of Egypt, and he made him governor over Egypt and all his household.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27128Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27128Q\"></sup>a famine came over all Egypt and Canaan, and great affliction <i>with it</i>, and our fathers could find no food.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27129R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27129R\"></sup>when Jacob heard that there was grain in Egypt, he sent our fathers <i>there</i> the first time.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>On the second <i>visit</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27130S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27130S\"></sup>Joseph made himself known to his brothers, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27130T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27130T\"></sup>Joseph’s family was disclosed to Pharaoh.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27131U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27131U\"></sup>Joseph sent <i>word</i> and invited Jacob his father and all his relatives to come to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27131V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27131V\"></sup>seventy-five <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27131W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27131W\"></sup>persons <i>in all</i>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27132X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27132X\"></sup>Jacob went down to Egypt and <i>there</i> he and our fathers died.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><i>From there</i> they were removed to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27133Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27133Y\"></sup>Shechem and laid in the tomb which Abraham had purchased for a sum of money from the sons of Hamor in Shechem.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“But as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27134Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27134Z\"></sup>time of the promise was approaching which God had assured to Abraham, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27134AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27134AA\"></sup>the people increased and multiplied in Egypt,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27135AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27135AB\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">there arose another king over Egypt who knew nothing about Joseph</span>.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>It was he who took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27136AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27136AC\"></sup>shrewd advantage of our race and mistreated our fathers so that they would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27136AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27136AD\"></sup>expose their infants and they would not survive.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>It was at this time that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27137AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27137AE\"></sup>Moses was born; and he was lovely in the sight of God, and he was nurtured three months in his father’s home.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And after he had been set outside, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27138AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27138AF\"></sup>Pharaoh’s daughter took him away and nurtured him as her own son.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Moses was educated in all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27139AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27139AG\"></sup>the learning of the Egyptians, and he was a man of power in words and deeds.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But when he was approaching the age of forty, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27140AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27140AH\"></sup>it entered his mind to visit his brethren, the sons of Israel.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And when he saw one <i>of them</i> being treated unjustly, he defended him and took vengeance for the oppressed by striking down the Egyptian.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And he supposed that his brethren understood that God was granting them deliverance through him, but they did not understand.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27143AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27143AI\"></sup>On the following day he appeared to them as they were fighting together, and he tried to reconcile them in peace, saying, ‘Men, you are brethren, why do you injure one another?’",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But the one who was injuring his neighbor pushed him away, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27144AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27144AJ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Who made you a ruler and judge over us</span>?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27145AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27145AK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You do not mean to kill me as you killed the Egyptian yesterday, do you</span>?’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>At this remark, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27146AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27146AL\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Moses fled and became an alien in the land of</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Midian</span>, where he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27146AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27146AM\"></sup>became the father of two sons.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“After forty years had passed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27147AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27147AN\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">an angel appeared to him in the wilderness of Mount</span> Sinai, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">in the flame of a burning thorn bush</span>.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>When Moses saw it, he marveled at the sight; and as he approached to look <i>more</i> closely, there came the voice of the Lord:",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27149AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27149AO\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">am the God of your fathers, the God of Abraham and Isaac and Jacob</span>.’ Moses shook with fear and would not venture to look.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27150AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27150AP\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">But the Lord said to him,</span> ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27150AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27150AQ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Take off the sandals from your feet, for the place on which you are standing is holy ground</span>.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27151AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27151AR\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">have certainly seen the oppression of My people in Egypt and have heard their groans, and I have come down to rescue them</span>; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27151AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27151AS\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">come now, and I will send you to Egypt</span>.’",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“This Moses whom they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27152AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27152AT\"></sup>disowned, saying, ‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Who made you a ruler and a judge</span>?’ is the one whom God sent <i>to be</i> both a ruler and a deliverer with the help of the angel who appeared to him in the thorn bush.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27153AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27153AU\"></sup>This man led them out, performing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27153AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27153AV\"></sup>wonders and signs in the land of Egypt and in the Red Sea and in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27153AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27153AW\"></sup>wilderness for forty years.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>This is the Moses who said to the sons of Israel, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27154AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27154AX\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God will raise up for you a prophet</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">like me from your brethren</span>.’",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>This is the one who was in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27155AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27155AY\"></sup>the congregation in the wilderness together with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27155AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27155AZ\"></sup>the angel who was speaking to him on Mount Sinai, and <i>who was</i> with our fathers; and he received <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27155BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27155BA\"></sup>living <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27155BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27155BB\"></sup>oracles to pass on to you.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Our fathers were unwilling to be obedient to him, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27156BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27156BC\"></sup>repudiated him and in their hearts turned back to Egypt,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27157BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27157BD\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">saying to Aaron, ‘Make for us gods who will go before us; for this Moses who led us out of the land of Egypt</span>—<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">we do not know what happened to him</span>.’",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>At that time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27158BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27158BE\"></sup>they made a calf and brought a sacrifice to the idol, and were rejoicing in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27158BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27158BF\"></sup>the works of their hands.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>But God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27159BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27159BG\"></sup>turned away and delivered them up to serve the host of heaven; as it is written in the book of the prophets, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27159BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27159BH\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">It was not to Me that you offered victims and sacrifices</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27159BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27159BI\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">forty years in the wilderness, was it</span>, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">house of Israel</span>?",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27160BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27160BJ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You also took along the tabernacle of Moloch and the star of the god</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Rompha, the images which you made to worship</span>. I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">also will remove you beyond Babylon</span>.’",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>“Our fathers had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27161BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27161BK\"></sup>the tabernacle of testimony in the wilderness, just as He who spoke to Moses directed <i>him</i> to make it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27161BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27161BL\"></sup>according to the pattern which he had seen.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>And having received it in their turn, our fathers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27162BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27162BM\"></sup>brought it in with Joshua upon dispossessing the nations whom God drove out before our fathers, until the time of David.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27163BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27163BN\"></sup><i>David</i> found favor in God’s sight, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27163BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27163BO\"></sup>asked that he might find a dwelling place for the God of Jacob.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>But it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27164BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27164BP\"></sup>Solomon who built a house for Him.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>However, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27165BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27165BQ\"></sup>the Most High does not dwell in <i>houses</i> made by <i>human</i> hands; as the prophet says:",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27166BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27166BR\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Heaven is My throne</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And earth is the footstool of My feet</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">What kind of house will you build for Me</span>?’ says the Lord,‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Or what place is there for My repose</span>?",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27167BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27167BS\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Was it not My hand which made all these things</span>?’",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>“You men who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27168BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27168BT\"></sup>stiff-necked and uncircumcised in heart and ears are always resisting the Holy Spirit; you are doing just as your fathers did.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27169BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27169BU\"></sup>Which one of the prophets did your fathers not persecute? They killed those who had previously announced the coming of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27169BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27169BV\"></sup>the Righteous One, whose betrayers and murderers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27169BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27169BW\"></sup>you have now become;",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>you who received the law as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27170BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27170BX\"></sup>ordained by angels, and <i>yet</i> did not keep it.”",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>Now when they heard this, they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27171BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27171BY\"></sup>cut to the quick, and they <i>began</i> gnashing their teeth at him.",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>But being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27172BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27172BZ\"></sup>full of the Holy Spirit, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27172CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27172CA\"></sup>gazed intently into heaven and saw the glory of God, and Jesus standing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27172CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27172CB\"></sup>at the right hand of God;",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>and he said, “Behold, I see the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27173CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27173CC\"></sup>heavens opened up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27173CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27173CD\"></sup>the Son of Man standing at the right hand of God.”",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>But they cried out with a loud voice, and covered their ears and rushed at him with one impulse.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>When they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27175CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27175CE\"></sup>driven him out of the city, they <i>began</i> stoning <i>him</i>; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27175CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27175CF\"></sup>the witnesses <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27175CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27175CG\"></sup>laid aside their robes at the feet of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27175CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27175CH\"></sup>a young man named Saul.",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>They went on stoning Stephen as he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27176CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27176CI\"></sup>called on <i>the Lord</i> and said, “Lord Jesus, receive my spirit!”",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27177CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27177CJ\"></sup>falling on his knees, he cried out with a loud voice, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27177CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27177CK\"></sup>do not hold this sin against them!” Having said this, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27177CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27177CL\"></sup>fell asleep."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27178A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27178A\"></sup>Saul was in hearty agreement with putting him to death.And on that day a great persecution began against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27178B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27178B\"></sup>the church in Jerusalem, and they were all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27178C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27178C\"></sup>scattered throughout the regions of Judea and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27178D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27178D\"></sup>Samaria, except the apostles.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><i>Some</i> devout men buried Stephen, and made loud lamentation over him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27180E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27180E\"></sup>Saul <i>began</i> ravaging the church, entering house after house, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27180F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27180F\"></sup>dragging off men and women, he would put them in prison.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Therefore, those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27181G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27181G\"></sup>who had been scattered went about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27181H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27181H\"></sup>preaching the word.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27182I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27182I\"></sup>Philip went down to the city of Samaria and <i>began</i> proclaiming Christ to them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The crowds with one accord were giving attention to what was said by Philip, as they heard and saw the signs which he was performing.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <i>in the case of</i> many who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27184J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27184J\"></sup>unclean spirits, they were coming out <i>of them</i> shouting with a loud voice; and many who had been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27184K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27184K\"></sup>paralyzed and lame were healed.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27185L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27185L\"></sup>much rejoicing in that city.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now there was a man named Simon, who formerly was practicing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27186M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27186M\"></sup>magic in the city and astonishing the people of Samaria, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27186N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27186N\"></sup>claiming to be someone great;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and they all, from smallest to greatest, were giving attention to him, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27187O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27187O\"></sup>This man is what is called the Great Power of God.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And they were giving him attention because he had for a long time astonished them with his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27188P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27188P\"></sup>magic arts.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But when they believed Philip <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27189Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27189Q\"></sup>preaching the good news about the kingdom of God and the name of Jesus Christ, they were being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27189R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27189R\"></sup>baptized, men and women alike.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Even Simon himself believed; and after being baptized, he continued on with Philip, and as he observed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27190S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27190S\"></sup>signs and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27190T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27190T\"></sup>great miracles taking place, he was constantly amazed.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Now when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27191U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27191U\"></sup>the apostles in Jerusalem heard that Samaria had received the word of God, they sent them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27191V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27191V\"></sup>Peter and John,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>who came down and prayed for them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27192W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27192W\"></sup>that they might receive the Holy Spirit.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For He had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27193X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27193X\"></sup>not yet fallen upon any of them; they had simply been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27193Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27193Y\"></sup>baptized in the name of the Lord Jesus.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27194Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27194Z\"></sup><i>began</i> laying their hands on them, and they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27194AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27194AA\"></sup>receiving the Holy Spirit.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now when Simon saw that the Spirit was bestowed through the laying on of the apostles’ hands, he offered them money,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>saying, “Give this authority to me as well, so that everyone on whom I lay my hands may receive the Holy Spirit.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But Peter said to him, “May your silver perish with you, because you thought you could <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27197AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27197AB\"></sup>obtain the gift of God with money!",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27198AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27198AC\"></sup>no part or portion in this matter, for your heart is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27198AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27198AD\"></sup>right before God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Therefore repent of this wickedness of yours, and pray the Lord that, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27199AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27199AE\"></sup>if possible, the intention of your heart may be forgiven you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For I see that you are in the gall of bitterness and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27200AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27200AF\"></sup>the bondage of iniquity.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But Simon answered and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27201AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27201AG\"></sup>Pray to the Lord for me yourselves, so that nothing of what you have said may come upon me.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So, when they had solemnly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27202AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27202AH\"></sup>testified and spoken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27202AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27202AI\"></sup>the word of the Lord, they started back to Jerusalem, and were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27202AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27202AJ\"></sup>preaching the gospel to many villages of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27202AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27202AK\"></sup>Samaritans.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27203AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27203AL\"></sup>an angel of the Lord spoke to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27203AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27203AM\"></sup>Philip saying, “Get up and go south to the road that descends from Jerusalem to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27203AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27203AN\"></sup>Gaza.” (This is a desert <i>road</i>.)",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>So he got up and went; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27204AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27204AO\"></sup>there was an Ethiopian eunuch, a court official of Candace, queen of the Ethiopians, who was in charge of all her treasure; and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27204AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27204AP\"></sup>had come to Jerusalem to worship,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>and he was returning and sitting in his chariot, and was reading the prophet Isaiah.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27206AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27206AQ\"></sup>the Spirit said to Philip, “Go up and join this chariot.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Philip ran up and heard him reading Isaiah the prophet, and said, “Do you understand what you are reading?”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And he said, “Well, how could I, unless someone guides me?” And he invited Philip to come up and sit with him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Now the passage of Scripture which he was reading was this:“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27209AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27209AR\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He was led as a sheep to slaughter</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And as a lamb before its shearer is silent</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">So He does not open His mouth</span>.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27210AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27210AS\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">In humiliation His judgment was taken away</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Who will</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">relate His</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">generation</span>?<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For His life is removed from the earth</span>.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>The eunuch answered Philip and said, “Please <i>tell me</i>, of whom does the prophet say this? Of himself or of someone else?”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Then Philip <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27212AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27212AT\"></sup>opened his mouth, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27212AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27212AU\"></sup>beginning from this Scripture he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27212AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27212AV\"></sup>preached Jesus to him.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>As they went along the road they came to some water; and the eunuch *said, “Look! Water! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27213AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27213AW\"></sup>What prevents me from being baptized?”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>[And Philip said, “If you believe with all your heart, you may.” And he answered and said, “I believe that Jesus Christ is the Son of God.”]",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And he ordered the chariot to stop; and they both went down into the water, Philip as well as the eunuch, and he baptized him.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>When they came up out of the water, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27216AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27216AX\"></sup>the Spirit of the Lord snatched Philip away; and the eunuch no longer saw him, but went on his way rejoicing.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>But Philip found himself at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27217AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27217AY\"></sup>Azotus, and as he passed through he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27217AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27217AZ\"></sup>kept preaching the gospel to all the cities until he came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27217BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27217BA\"></sup>Caesarea."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27218A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27218A\"></sup>Now Saul, still <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27218B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27218B\"></sup>breathing threats and murder against the disciples of the Lord, went to the high priest,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and asked for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27219C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27219C\"></sup>letters from him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27219D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27219D\"></sup>the synagogues at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27219E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27219E\"></sup>Damascus, so that if he found any belonging to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27219F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27219F\"></sup>the Way, both men and women, he might bring them bound to Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>As he was traveling, it happened that he was approaching Damascus, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27220G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27220G\"></sup>suddenly a light from heaven flashed around him;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27221H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27221H\"></sup>he fell to the ground and heard a voice saying to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Saul, Saul, why are you persecuting Me?”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And he said, “Who are You, Lord?” And He <i>said</i>, <span class=\"woj\">“I am Jesus whom you are persecuting,</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>but get up and enter the city, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27223I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27223I\"></sup>it will be told you what you must do.”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The men who traveled with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27224J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27224J\"></sup>stood speechless, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27224K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27224K\"></sup>hearing the voice but seeing no one.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Saul got up from the ground, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27225L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27225L\"></sup>though his eyes were open, he could see nothing; and leading him by the hand, they brought him into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27225M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27225M\"></sup>Damascus.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And he was three days without sight, and neither ate nor drank.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now there was a disciple at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27227N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27227N\"></sup>Damascus named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27227O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27227O\"></sup>Ananias; and the Lord said to him in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27227P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27227P\"></sup>a vision, <span class=\"woj\">“Ananias.”</span> And he said, “Here I am, Lord.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the Lord <i>said</i> to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Get up and go to the street called Straight, and inquire at the house of Judas for a man from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27228Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27228Q\"></sup>Tarsus named Saul, for he is praying,</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and he has seen in a vision a man named Ananias come in and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27229R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27229R\"></sup>lay his hands on him, so that he might regain his sight.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But Ananias answered, “Lord, I have heard from many about this man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27230S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27230S\"></sup>how much harm he did to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27230T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27230T\"></sup>Your saints at Jerusalem;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and here he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27231U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27231U\"></sup>has authority from the chief priests to bind all who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27231V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27231V\"></sup>call on Your name.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But the Lord said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Go, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27232W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27232W\"></sup>he is a chosen instrument of Mine, to bear My name before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27232X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27232X\"></sup>the Gentiles and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27232Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27232Y\"></sup>kings and the sons of Israel;</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27233Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27233Z\"></sup>I will show him how much he must suffer for My name’s sake.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So Ananias departed and entered the house, and after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27234AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27234AA\"></sup>laying his hands on him said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27234AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27234AB\"></sup>Brother Saul, the Lord Jesus, who appeared to you on the road by which you were coming, has sent me so that you may regain your sight and be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27234AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27234AC\"></sup>filled with the Holy Spirit.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And immediately there fell from his eyes something like scales, and he regained his sight, and he got up and was baptized;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and he took food and was strengthened.Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27236AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27236AD\"></sup>for several days he was with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27236AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27236AE\"></sup>the disciples who were at Damascus,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and immediately he <i>began</i> to proclaim Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27237AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27237AF\"></sup>in the synagogues, saying, “He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27237AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27237AG\"></sup>the Son of God.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>All those hearing him continued to be amazed, and were saying, “Is this not he who in Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27238AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27238AH\"></sup>destroyed those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27238AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27238AI\"></sup>called on this name, and <i>who</i> had come here for the purpose of bringing them bound before the chief priests?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But Saul kept increasing in strength and confounding the Jews who lived at Damascus by proving that this <i>Jesus</i> is the Christ.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27240AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27240AJ\"></sup>many days had elapsed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27240AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27240AK\"></sup>the Jews plotted together to do away with him,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27241AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27241AL\"></sup>their plot became known to Saul. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27241AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27241AM\"></sup>They were also watching the gates day and night so that they might put him to death;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>but his disciples took him by night and let him down through <i>an opening in</i> the wall, lowering him in a large basket.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27243AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27243AN\"></sup>When he came to Jerusalem, he was trying to associate with the disciples; but they were all afraid of him, not believing that he was a disciple.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27244AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27244AO\"></sup>Barnabas took hold of him and brought him to the apostles and described to them how he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27244AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27244AP\"></sup>seen the Lord on the road, and that He had talked to him, and how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27244AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27244AQ\"></sup>at Damascus he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27244AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27244AR\"></sup>spoken out boldly in the name of Jesus.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And he was with them, moving about freely in Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27245AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27245AS\"></sup>speaking out boldly in the name of the Lord.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And he was talking and arguing with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27246AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27246AT\"></sup>Hellenistic <i>Jews</i>; but they were attempting to put him to death.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27247AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27247AU\"></sup>the brethren learned <i>of it</i>, they brought him down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27247AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27247AV\"></sup>Caesarea and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27247AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27247AW\"></sup>sent him away to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27247AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27247AX\"></sup>Tarsus.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27248AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27248AY\"></sup>the church throughout all Judea and Galilee and Samaria enjoyed peace, being built up; and going on in the fear of the Lord and in the comfort of the Holy Spirit, it continued to increase.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Now as Peter was traveling through all <i>those regions</i>, he came down also to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27249AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27249AZ\"></sup>the saints who lived at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27249BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27249BA\"></sup>Lydda.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>There he found a man named Aeneas, who had been bedridden eight years, for he was paralyzed.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Peter said to him, “Aeneas, Jesus Christ heals you; get up and make your bed.” Immediately he got up.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And all who lived at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27252BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27252BB\"></sup>Lydda and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27252BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27252BC\"></sup>Sharon saw him, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27252BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27252BD\"></sup>turned to the Lord.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Now in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27253BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27253BE\"></sup>Joppa there was a disciple named Tabitha (which translated <i>in Greek</i> is called Dorcas); this woman was abounding with deeds of kindness and charity which she continually did.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And it happened at that time that she fell sick and died; and when they had washed her body, they laid it in an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27254BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27254BF\"></sup>upper room.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Since Lydda was near <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27255BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27255BG\"></sup>Joppa, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27255BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27255BH\"></sup>the disciples, having heard that Peter was there, sent two men to him, imploring him, “Do not delay in coming to us.”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>So Peter arose and went with them. When he arrived, they brought him into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27256BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27256BI\"></sup>upper room; and all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27256BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27256BJ\"></sup>widows stood beside him, weeping and showing all the tunics and garments that Dorcas used to make while she was with them.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>But Peter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27257BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27257BK\"></sup>sent them all out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27257BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27257BL\"></sup>knelt down and prayed, and turning to the body, he said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27257BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27257BM\"></sup>Tabitha, arise.” And she opened her eyes, and when she saw Peter, she sat up.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And he gave her his hand and raised her up; and calling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27258BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27258BN\"></sup>the saints and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27258BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27258BO\"></sup>widows, he presented her alive.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>It became known all over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27259BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27259BP\"></sup>Joppa, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27259BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27259BQ\"></sup>many believed in the Lord.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And Peter stayed many days in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27260BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27260BR\"></sup>Joppa with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27260BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27260BS\"></sup>a tanner <i>named</i> Simon."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Now <i>there was</i> a man at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27261A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27261A\"></sup>Caesarea named Cornelius, a centurion of what was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27261B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27261B\"></sup>called the Italian cohort,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>a devout man and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27262C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27262C\"></sup>one who feared God with all his household, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27262D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27262D\"></sup>gave many alms to the <i>Jewish</i> people and prayed to God continually.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>About <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27263E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27263E\"></sup>the ninth hour of the day he clearly saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27263F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27263F\"></sup>in a vision <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27263G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27263G\"></sup>an angel of God who had <i>just</i> come in and said to him, “Cornelius!”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27264H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27264H\"></sup>fixing his gaze on him and being much alarmed, he said, “What is it, Lord?” And he said to him, “Your prayers and alms <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27264I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27264I\"></sup>have ascended <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27264J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27264J\"></sup>as a memorial before God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now dispatch <i>some</i> men to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27265K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27265K\"></sup>Joppa and send for a man <i>named</i> Simon, who is also called Peter;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>he is staying with a tanner <i>named</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27266L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27266L\"></sup>Simon, whose house is by the sea.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the angel who was speaking to him had left, he summoned two of his servants and a devout soldier of those who were his personal attendants,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and after he had explained everything to them, he sent them to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27268M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27268M\"></sup>Joppa.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>On the next day, as they were on their way and approaching the city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27269N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27269N\"></sup>Peter went up on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27269O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27269O\"></sup>the housetop about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27269P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27269P\"></sup>the sixth hour to pray.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But he became hungry and was desiring to eat; but while they were making preparations, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27270Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27270Q\"></sup>fell into a trance;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and he *saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27271R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27271R\"></sup>the sky opened up, and an object like a great sheet coming down, lowered by four corners to the ground,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and there were in it all <i>kinds of</i> four-footed animals and crawling creatures of the earth and birds of the air.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>A voice came to him, “Get up, Peter, kill and eat!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But Peter said, “By no means, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27274S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27274S\"></sup>Lord, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27274T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27274T\"></sup>I have never eaten anything unholy and unclean.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Again a voice <i>came</i> to him a second time, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27275U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27275U\"></sup>What God has cleansed, no <i>longer</i> consider unholy.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This happened three times, and immediately the object was taken up into the sky.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now while Peter was greatly perplexed in mind as to what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27277V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27277V\"></sup>the vision which he had seen might be, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27277W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27277W\"></sup>the men who had been sent by Cornelius, having asked directions for Simon’s house, appeared at the gate;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and calling out, they were asking whether Simon, who was also called Peter, was staying there.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>While Peter was reflecting on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27279X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27279X\"></sup>the vision, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27279Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27279Y\"></sup>the Spirit said to him, “Behold, three men are looking for you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But get up, go downstairs and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27280Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27280Z\"></sup>accompany them without misgivings, for I have sent them Myself.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Peter went down to the men and said, “Behold, I am the one you are looking for; what is the reason for which you have come?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>They said, “Cornelius, a centurion, a righteous and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27282AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27282AA\"></sup>God-fearing man well spoken of by the entire nation of the Jews, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27282AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27282AB\"></sup>was <i>divinely</i> directed by a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27282AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27282AC\"></sup>holy angel to send for you <i>to come</i> to his house and hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27282AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27282AD\"></sup>a message from you.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>So he invited them in and gave them lodging.And on the next day he got up and went away with them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27283AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27283AE\"></sup>some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27283AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27283AF\"></sup>the brethren from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27283AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27283AG\"></sup>Joppa accompanied him.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>On the following day he entered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27284AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27284AH\"></sup>Caesarea. Now Cornelius was waiting for them and had called together his relatives and close friends.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When Peter entered, Cornelius met him, and fell at his feet and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27285AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27285AI\"></sup>worshiped <i>him</i>.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But Peter raised him up, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27286AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27286AJ\"></sup>Stand up; I too am <i>just</i> a man.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>As he talked with him, he entered and *found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27287AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27287AK\"></sup>many people assembled.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And he said to them, “You yourselves know how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27288AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27288AL\"></sup>unlawful it is for a man who is a Jew to associate with a foreigner or to visit him; and <i>yet</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27288AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27288AM\"></sup>God has shown me that I should not call any man unholy or unclean.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>That is why I came without even raising any objection when I was sent for. So I ask for what reason you have sent for me.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Cornelius said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27290AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27290AN\"></sup>Four days ago to this hour, I was praying in my house during <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27290AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27290AO\"></sup>the ninth hour; and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27290AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27290AP\"></sup>a man stood before me in shining garments,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>and he *said, ‘Cornelius, your prayer has been heard and your alms have been remembered before God.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Therefore send to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27292AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27292AQ\"></sup>Joppa and invite Simon, who is also called Peter, to come to you; he is staying at the house of Simon <i>the</i> tanner by the sea.’",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So I sent for you immediately, and you have been kind enough to come. Now then, we are all here present before God to hear all that you have been commanded by the Lord.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27294AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27294AR\"></sup>Opening his mouth, Peter said:“I most certainly understand <i>now</i> that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27294AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27294AS\"></sup>God is not one to show partiality,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27295AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27295AT\"></sup>in every nation the man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27295AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27295AU\"></sup>fears Him and does what is right is welcome to Him.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>The word which He sent to the sons of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27296AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27296AV\"></sup>preaching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27296AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27296AW\"></sup>peace through Jesus Christ (He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27296AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27296AX\"></sup>Lord of all)—",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>you yourselves know the thing which took place throughout all Judea, starting from Galilee, after the baptism which John proclaimed.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><i>You know of</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27298AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27298AY\"></sup>Jesus of Nazareth, how God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27298AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27298AZ\"></sup>anointed Him with the Holy Spirit and with power, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27298BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27298BA\"></sup>and <i>how</i> He went about doing good and healing all who were oppressed by the devil, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27298BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27298BB\"></sup>God was with Him.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>We are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27299BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27299BC\"></sup>witnesses of all the things He did both in the land of the Jews and in Jerusalem. They also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27299BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27299BD\"></sup>put Him to death by hanging Him on a cross.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27300BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27300BE\"></sup>God raised Him up on the third day and granted that He become visible,",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27301BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27301BF\"></sup>not to all the people, but to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27301BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27301BG\"></sup>witnesses who were chosen beforehand by God, <i>that is</i>, to us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27301BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27301BH\"></sup>who ate and drank with Him after He arose from the dead.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27302BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27302BI\"></sup>ordered us to preach to the people, and solemnly to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27302BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27302BJ\"></sup>testify that this is the One who has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27302BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27302BK\"></sup>appointed by God as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27302BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27302BL\"></sup>Judge of the living and the dead.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Of Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27303BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27303BM\"></sup>all the prophets bear witness that through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27303BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27303BN\"></sup>His name everyone who believes in Him receives forgiveness of sins.”",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>While Peter was still speaking these words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27304BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27304BO\"></sup>the Holy Spirit fell upon all those who were listening to the message.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27305BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27305BP\"></sup>All the circumcised believers who came with Peter were amazed, because the gift of the Holy Spirit had been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27305BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27305BQ\"></sup>poured out on the Gentiles also.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>For they were hearing them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27306BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27306BR\"></sup>speaking with tongues and exalting God. Then Peter answered,",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27307BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27307BS\"></sup>Surely no one can refuse the water for these to be baptized who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27307BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27307BT\"></sup>have received the Holy Spirit just as we <i>did</i>, can he?”",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27308BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27308BU\"></sup>ordered them to be baptized <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27308BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27308BV\"></sup>in the name of Jesus Christ. Then they asked him to stay on for a few days."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Now the apostles and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27309A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27309A\"></sup>the brethren who were throughout Judea heard that the Gentiles also had received the word of God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And when Peter came up to Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27310B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27310B\"></sup>those who were circumcised took issue with him,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27311C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27311C\"></sup>You went to uncircumcised men and ate with them.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But Peter began <i>speaking</i> and <i>proceeded</i> to explain to them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27312D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27312D\"></sup>in orderly sequence, saying,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27313E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27313E\"></sup>I was in the city of Joppa praying; and in a trance I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27313F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27313F\"></sup>a vision, an object coming down like a great sheet lowered by four corners from the sky; and it came right down to me,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and when I had fixed my gaze on it and was observing it I saw the four-footed animals of the earth and the wild beasts and the crawling creatures and the birds of the air.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I also heard a voice saying to me, ‘Get up, Peter; kill and eat.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But I said, ‘By no means, Lord, for nothing unholy or unclean has ever entered my mouth.’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But a voice from heaven answered a second time, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27317G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27317G\"></sup>What God has cleansed, no longer consider unholy.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This happened three times, and everything was drawn back up into the sky.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And behold, at that moment three men appeared at the house in which we were <i>staying</i>, having been sent to me from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27319H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27319H\"></sup>Caesarea.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27320I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27320I\"></sup>The Spirit told me to go with them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27320J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27320J\"></sup>without misgivings. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27320K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27320K\"></sup>These six brethren also went with me and we entered the man’s house.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And he reported to us how he had seen the angel standing in his house, and saying, ‘Send to Joppa and have Simon, who is also called Peter, brought here;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and he will speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27322L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27322L\"></sup>words to you by which you will be saved, you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27322M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27322M\"></sup>all your household.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And as I began to speak, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27323N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27323N\"></sup>the Holy Spirit fell upon them just <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27323O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27323O\"></sup>as <i>He did</i> upon us at the beginning.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And I remembered the word of the Lord, how He used to say, <span class=\"woj\">‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27324P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27324P\"></sup>John baptized with water, but you will be baptized with the Holy Spirit.’</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27325Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27325Q\"></sup>God gave to them the same gift as <i>He gave</i> to us also after believing in the Lord Jesus Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27325R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27325R\"></sup>who was I that I could stand in God’s way?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When they heard this, they quieted down and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27326S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27326S\"></sup>glorified God, saying, “Well then, God has granted to the Gentiles also the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27326T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27326T\"></sup>repentance <i>that leads</i> to life.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27327U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27327U\"></sup>So then those who were scattered because of the persecution that occurred in connection with Stephen made their way to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27327V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27327V\"></sup>Phoenicia and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27327W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27327W\"></sup>Cyprus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27327X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27327X\"></sup>Antioch, speaking the word to no one except to Jews alone.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But there were some of them, men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27328Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27328Y\"></sup>Cyprus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27328Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27328Z\"></sup>Cyrene, who came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27328AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27328AA\"></sup>Antioch and <i>began</i> speaking to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27328AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27328AB\"></sup>Greeks also, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27328AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27328AC\"></sup>preaching the Lord Jesus.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27329AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27329AD\"></sup>the hand of the Lord was with them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27329AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27329AE\"></sup>a large number who believed turned to the Lord.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The news about them reached the ears of the church at Jerusalem, and they sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27330AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27330AF\"></sup>Barnabas off to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27330AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27330AG\"></sup>Antioch.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then when he arrived and witnessed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27331AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27331AH\"></sup>the grace of God, he rejoiced and <i>began</i> to encourage them all with resolute heart to remain <i>true</i> to the Lord;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>for he was a good man, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27332AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27332AI\"></sup>full of the Holy Spirit and of faith. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27332AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27332AJ\"></sup>considerable numbers were brought to the Lord.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And he left for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27333AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27333AK\"></sup>Tarsus to look for Saul;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and when he had found him, he brought him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27334AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27334AL\"></sup>Antioch. And for an entire year they met with the church and taught considerable numbers; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27334AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27334AM\"></sup>the disciples were first called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27334AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27334AN\"></sup>Christians in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27334AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27334AO\"></sup>Antioch.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Now at this time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27335AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27335AP\"></sup>some prophets came down from Jerusalem to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27335AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27335AQ\"></sup>Antioch.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>One of them named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27336AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27336AR\"></sup>Agabus stood up and <i>began</i> to indicate by the Spirit that there would certainly be a great famine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27336AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27336AS\"></sup>all over the world. And this took place in the <i>reign</i> of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27336AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27336AT\"></sup>Claudius.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And in the proportion that any of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27337AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27337AU\"></sup>the disciples had means, each of them determined to send <i>a contribution</i> for the relief of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27337AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27337AV\"></sup>the brethren living in Judea.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27338AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27338AW\"></sup>And this they did, sending it in charge of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27338AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27338AX\"></sup>Barnabas and Saul to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27338AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27338AY\"></sup>elders."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Now about that time Herod the king laid hands on some who belonged to the church in order to mistreat them.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27340A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27340A\"></sup>had James the brother of John <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27340B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27340B\"></sup>put to death with a sword.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When he saw that it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27341C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27341C\"></sup>pleased the Jews, he proceeded to arrest Peter also. Now it was during <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27341D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27341D\"></sup>the days of Unleavened Bread.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When he had seized him, he put him in prison, delivering him to four <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27342E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27342E\"></sup>squads of soldiers to guard him, intending after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27342F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27342F\"></sup>the Passover to bring him out before the people.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So Peter was kept in the prison, but prayer for him was being made fervently by the church to God.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On the very night when Herod was about to bring him forward, Peter was sleeping between two soldiers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27344G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27344G\"></sup>bound with two chains, and guards in front of the door were watching over the prison.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27345H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27345H\"></sup>an angel of the Lord suddenly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27345I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27345I\"></sup>appeared and a light shone in the cell; and he struck Peter’s side and woke him up, saying, “Get up quickly.” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27345J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27345J\"></sup>his chains fell off his hands.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the angel said to him, “Gird yourself and put on your sandals.” And he did so. And he *said to him, “Wrap your cloak around you and follow me.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And he went out and continued to follow, and he did not know that what was being done by the angel was real, but thought he was seeing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27347K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27347K\"></sup>a vision.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When they had passed the first and second guard, they came to the iron gate that leads into the city, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27348L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27348L\"></sup>opened for them by itself; and they went out and went along one street, and immediately the angel departed from him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When Peter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27349M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27349M\"></sup>came to himself, he said, “Now I know for sure that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27349N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27349N\"></sup>the Lord has sent forth His angel and rescued me from the hand of Herod and from all that the Jewish people were expecting.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And when he realized <i>this</i>, he went to the house of Mary, the mother of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27350O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27350O\"></sup>John who was also called Mark, where many were gathered together and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27350P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27350P\"></sup>were praying.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When he knocked at the door of the gate, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27351Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27351Q\"></sup>a servant-girl named Rhoda came to answer.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>When she recognized Peter’s voice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27352R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27352R\"></sup>because of her joy she did not open the gate, but ran in and announced that Peter was standing in front of the gate.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They said to her, “You are out of your mind!” But she kept insisting that it was so. They kept saying, “It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27353S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27353S\"></sup>his angel.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But Peter continued knocking; and when they had opened <i>the door</i>, they saw him and were amazed.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27355T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27355T\"></sup>motioning to them with his hand to be silent, he described to them how the Lord had led him out of the prison. And he said, “Report these things to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27355U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27355U\"></sup>James and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27355V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27355V\"></sup>the brethren.” Then he left and went to another place.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now when day came, there was no small disturbance among the soldiers <i>as to</i> what could have become of Peter.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When Herod had searched for him and had not found him, he examined the guards and ordered that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27357W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27357W\"></sup>be led away <i>to execution</i>. Then he went down from Judea to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27357X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27357X\"></sup>Caesarea and was spending time there.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now he was very angry with the people of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27358Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27358Y\"></sup>Tyre and Sidon; and with one accord they came to him, and having won over Blastus the king’s chamberlain, they were asking for peace, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27358Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27358Z\"></sup>their country was fed by the king’s country.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>On an appointed day Herod, having put on his royal apparel, took his seat on the rostrum and <i>began</i> delivering an address to them.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The people kept crying out, “The voice of a god and not of a man!”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27361AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27361AA\"></sup>an angel of the Lord struck him because he did not give God the glory, and he was eaten by worms and died.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27362AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27362AB\"></sup>the word of the Lord continued to grow and to be multiplied.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27363AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27363AC\"></sup>Barnabas and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27363AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27363AD\"></sup>Saul returned from Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27363AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27363AE\"></sup>when they had fulfilled their mission, taking along with <i>them</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27363AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27363AF\"></sup>John, who was also called Mark."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>Now there were at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27364A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27364A\"></sup>Antioch, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27364B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27364B\"></sup>church that was <i>there</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27364C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27364C\"></sup>prophets and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27364D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27364D\"></sup>teachers: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27364E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27364E\"></sup>Barnabas, and Simeon who was called Niger, and Lucius of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27364F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27364F\"></sup>Cyrene, and Manaen who had been brought up with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27364G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27364G\"></sup>Herod the tetrarch, and Saul.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>While they were ministering to the Lord and fasting, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27365H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27365H\"></sup>the Holy Spirit said, “Set apart for Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27365I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27365I\"></sup>Barnabas and Saul for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27365J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27365J\"></sup>the work to which I have called them.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then, when they had fasted and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27366K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27366K\"></sup>prayed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27366L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27366L\"></sup>laid their hands on them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27366M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27366M\"></sup>they sent them away.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27367N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27367N\"></sup>sent out by the Holy Spirit, they went down to Seleucia and from there they sailed to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27367O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27367O\"></sup>Cyprus.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When they reached Salamis, they <i>began</i> to proclaim the word of God in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27368P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27368P\"></sup>the synagogues of the Jews; and they also had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27368Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27368Q\"></sup>John as their helper.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When they had gone through the whole island as far as Paphos, they found a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27369R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27369R\"></sup>magician, a Jewish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27369S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27369S\"></sup>false prophet whose name was Bar-Jesus,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>who was with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27370T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27370T\"></sup>proconsul, Sergius Paulus, a man of intelligence. This man summoned Barnabas and Saul and sought to hear the word of God.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But Elymas the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27371U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27371U\"></sup>magician (for so his name is translated) was opposing them, seeking to turn the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27371V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27371V\"></sup>proconsul away from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27371W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27371W\"></sup>the faith.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But Saul, who was also <i>known as</i> Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27372X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27372X\"></sup>filled with the Holy Spirit, fixed his gaze on him,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and said, “You who are full of all deceit and fraud, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27373Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27373Y\"></sup>son of the devil, you enemy of all righteousness, will you not cease to make crooked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27373Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27373Z\"></sup>the straight ways of the Lord?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27374AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27374AA\"></sup>the hand of the Lord is upon you, and you will be blind and not see the sun for a time.” And immediately a mist and a darkness fell upon him, and he went about seeking those who would lead him by the hand.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27375AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27375AB\"></sup>proconsul believed when he saw what had happened, being amazed at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27375AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27375AC\"></sup>the teaching of the Lord.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now Paul and his companions put out to sea from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27376AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27376AD\"></sup>Paphos and came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27376AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27376AE\"></sup>Perga in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27376AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27376AF\"></sup>Pamphylia; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27376AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27376AG\"></sup>John left them and returned to Jerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But going on from Perga, they arrived at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27377AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27377AH\"></sup>Pisidian <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27377AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27377AI\"></sup>Antioch, and on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27377AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27377AJ\"></sup>the Sabbath day they went into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27377AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27377AK\"></sup>the synagogue and sat down.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>After <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27378AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27378AL\"></sup>the reading of the Law and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27378AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27378AM\"></sup>the Prophets <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27378AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27378AN\"></sup>the synagogue officials sent to them, saying, “Brethren, if you have any word of exhortation for the people, say it.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Paul stood up, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27379AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27379AO\"></sup>motioning with his hand said,“Men of Israel, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27379AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27379AP\"></sup>you who fear God, listen:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The God of this people Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27380AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27380AQ\"></sup>chose our fathers and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27380AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27380AR\"></sup>made the people great during their stay in the land of Egypt, and with an uplifted arm <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27380AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27380AS\"></sup>He led them out from it.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27381AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27381AT\"></sup>a period of about forty years <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27381AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27381AU\"></sup>He put up with them in the wilderness.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27382AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27382AV\"></sup>When He had destroyed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27382AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27382AW\"></sup>seven nations in the land of Canaan, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27382AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27382AX\"></sup>distributed their land as an inheritance—<i>all of which took</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27382AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27382AY\"></sup>about four hundred and fifty years.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>After these things He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27383AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27383AZ\"></sup>gave <i>them</i> judges until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27383BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27383BA\"></sup>Samuel the prophet.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27384BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27384BB\"></sup>asked for a king, and God gave them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27384BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27384BC\"></sup>Saul the son of Kish, a man of the tribe of Benjamin, for forty years.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>After He had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27385BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27385BD\"></sup>removed him, He raised up David to be their king, concerning whom He also testified and said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27385BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27385BE\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">have found David</span> the son of Jesse, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">a man after My heart</span>, who will do all My will.’",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27386BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27386BF\"></sup>From the descendants of this man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27386BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27386BG\"></sup>according to promise, God has brought to Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27386BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27386BH\"></sup>a Savior, Jesus,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27387BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27387BI\"></sup>John had proclaimed before His coming a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27387BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27387BJ\"></sup>baptism of repentance to all the people of Israel.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And while John <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27388BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27388BK\"></sup>was completing his course, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27388BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27388BL\"></sup>he kept saying, ‘What do you suppose that I am? I am not <i>He</i>. But behold, one is coming after me the sandals of whose feet I am not worthy to untie.’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Brethren, sons of Abraham’s family, and those among you who fear God, to us the message of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27389BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27389BM\"></sup>this salvation has been sent.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For those who live in Jerusalem, and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27390BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27390BN\"></sup>rulers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27390BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27390BO\"></sup>recognizing neither Him nor the utterances of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27390BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27390BP\"></sup>the prophets which are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27390BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27390BQ\"></sup>read every Sabbath, fulfilled <i>these</i> by condemning <i>Him</i>.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And though they found no ground for <i>putting Him to</i> death, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27391BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27391BR\"></sup>asked Pilate that He be executed.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>When they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27392BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27392BS\"></sup>carried out all that was written concerning Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27392BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27392BT\"></sup>they took Him down from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27392BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27392BU\"></sup>the cross and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27392BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27392BV\"></sup>laid Him in a tomb.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27393BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27393BW\"></sup>raised Him from the dead;",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>and for many days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27394BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27394BX\"></sup>He appeared to those who came up with Him from Galilee to Jerusalem, the very ones who are now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27394BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27394BY\"></sup>His witnesses to the people.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27395BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27395BZ\"></sup>preach to you the good news of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27395CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27395CA\"></sup>the promise made to the fathers,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>that God has fulfilled this <i>promise</i> to our children in that He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27396CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27396CB\"></sup>raised up Jesus, as it is also written in the second Psalm, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27396CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27396CC\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You are My Son; today i have begotten You</span>.’",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><i>As for the fact</i> that He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27397CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27397CD\"></sup>raised Him up from the dead, no longer to return to decay, He has spoken in this way: ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27397CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27397CE\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will give you the holy</span> <i>and</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">sure</span> <i>blessings</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">of David</span>.’",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Therefore He also says in another <i>Psalm</i>, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27398CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27398CF\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You will not</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">allow Your</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Holy One to</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">undergo decay</span>.’",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27399CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27399CG\"></sup>David, after he had served <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27399CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27399CH\"></sup>the purpose of God in his own generation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27399CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27399CI\"></sup>fell asleep, and was laid among his fathers and underwent decay;",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>but He whom God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27400CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27400CJ\"></sup>raised did not undergo decay.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Therefore let it be known to you, brethren, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27401CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27401CK\"></sup>through Him forgiveness of sins is proclaimed to you,",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>and through Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27402CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27402CL\"></sup>everyone who believes is freed from all things, from which you could not be freed through the Law of Moses.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Therefore take heed, so that the thing spoken of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27403CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27403CM\"></sup>in the Prophets may not come upon <i>you</i>:",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27404CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27404CN\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Behold, you scoffers, and marvel, and</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">perish</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For I am accomplishing a work in your days</span>,A <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">work which you will never believe, though someone should describe it to you</span>.’”",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>As Paul and Barnabas were going out, the people kept begging that these things might be spoken to them the next <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27405CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27405CO\"></sup>Sabbath.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Now when <i>the meeting of</i> the synagogue had broken up, many of the Jews and of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27406CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27406CP\"></sup>God-fearing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27406CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27406CQ\"></sup>proselytes followed Paul and Barnabas, who, speaking to them, were urging them to continue in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27406CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27406CR\"></sup>the grace of God.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>The next <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27407CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27407CS\"></sup>Sabbath nearly the whole city assembled to hear the word of the Lord.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27408CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27408CT\"></sup>the Jews saw the crowds, they were filled with jealousy and <i>began</i> contradicting the things spoken by Paul, and were blaspheming.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Paul and Barnabas spoke out boldly and said, “It was necessary that the word of God be spoken to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27409CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27409CU\"></sup>first; since you repudiate it and judge yourselves unworthy of eternal life, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27409CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27409CV\"></sup>we are turning to the Gentiles.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>For so the Lord has commanded us,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27410CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27410CW\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">have placed You as a</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27410CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27410CX\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">light for the Gentiles</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">That You may</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">bring salvation to the end of the earth</span>.’”",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>When the Gentiles heard this, they <i>began</i> rejoicing and glorifying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27411CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27411CY\"></sup>the word of the Lord; and as many as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27411CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27411CZ\"></sup>had been appointed to eternal life believed.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27412DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27412DA\"></sup>the word of the Lord was being spread through the whole region.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27413DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27413DB\"></sup>the Jews incited the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27413DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27413DC\"></sup>devout women <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27413DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27413DD\"></sup>of prominence and the leading men of the city, and instigated a persecution against Paul and Barnabas, and drove them out of their district.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27414DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27414DE\"></sup>they shook off the dust of their feet <i>in protest</i> against them and went to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27414DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27414DF\"></sup>Iconium.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>And the disciples were continually <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27415DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27415DG\"></sup>filled with joy and with the Holy Spirit."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27416A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27416A\"></sup>Iconium <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27416B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27416B\"></sup>they entered the synagogue of the Jews together, and spoke in such a manner <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27416C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27416C\"></sup>that a large number of people believed, both of Jews and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27416D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27416D\"></sup>Greeks.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27417E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27417E\"></sup>the Jews who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27417F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27417F\"></sup>disbelieved stirred up the minds of the Gentiles and embittered them against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27417G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27417G\"></sup>the brethren.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore they spent a long time <i>there</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27418H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27418H\"></sup>speaking boldly <i>with reliance</i> upon the Lord, who was testifying to the word of His grace, granting that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27418I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27418I\"></sup>signs and wonders be done by their hands.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27419J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27419J\"></sup>But the people of the city were divided; and some sided with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27419K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27419K\"></sup>the Jews, and some with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27419L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27419L\"></sup>the apostles.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And when an attempt was made by both the Gentiles and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27420M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27420M\"></sup>the Jews with their rulers, to mistreat and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27420N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27420N\"></sup>stone them,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>they became aware of it and fled to the cities of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27421O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27421O\"></sup>Lycaonia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27421P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27421P\"></sup>Lystra and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27421Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27421Q\"></sup>Derbe, and the surrounding region;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and there they continued to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27422R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27422R\"></sup>preach the gospel.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>At <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27423S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27423S\"></sup>Lystra <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27423T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27423T\"></sup>a man was sitting who had no strength in his feet, lame from his mother’s womb, who had never walked.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>This man was listening to Paul as he spoke, who, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27424U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27424U\"></sup>when he had fixed his gaze on him and had seen that he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27424V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27424V\"></sup>faith to be made well,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>said with a loud voice, “Stand upright on your feet.” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27425W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27425W\"></sup>And he leaped up and <i>began</i> to walk.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When the crowds saw what Paul had done, they raised their voice, saying in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27426X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27426X\"></sup>Lycaonian language, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27426Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27426Y\"></sup>The gods have become like men and have come down to us.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And they <i>began</i> calling Barnabas, Zeus, and Paul, Hermes, because he was the chief speaker.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The priest of Zeus, whose <i>temple</i> was just outside the city, brought oxen and garlands to the gates, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27428Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27428Z\"></sup>wanted to offer sacrifice with the crowds.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27429AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27429AA\"></sup>the apostles Barnabas and Paul heard of it, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27429AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27429AB\"></sup>tore their robes and rushed out into the crowd, crying out",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and saying, “Men, why are you doing these things? We are also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27430AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27430AC\"></sup>men of the same nature as you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27430AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27430AD\"></sup>preach the gospel to you that you should turn from these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27430AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27430AE\"></sup>vain things to a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27430AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27430AF\"></sup>living God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27430AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27430AG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">who made the heaven and the earth and the sea and all that is in them</span>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In the generations gone by He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27431AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27431AH\"></sup>permitted all the nations to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27431AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27431AI\"></sup>go their own ways;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27432AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27432AJ\"></sup>He did not leave Himself without witness, in that He did good and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27432AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27432AK\"></sup>gave you rains from heaven and fruitful seasons, satisfying your hearts with food and gladness.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><i>Even</i> saying these things, with difficulty they restrained the crowds from offering sacrifice to them.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27434AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27434AL\"></sup>Jews came from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27434AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27434AM\"></sup>Antioch and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27434AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27434AN\"></sup>Iconium, and having won over the crowds, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27434AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27434AO\"></sup>stoned Paul and dragged him out of the city, supposing him to be dead.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27435AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27435AP\"></sup>the disciples stood around him, he got up and entered the city. The next day he went away with Barnabas to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27435AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27435AQ\"></sup>Derbe.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>After they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27436AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27436AR\"></sup>preached the gospel to that city and had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27436AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27436AS\"></sup>made many disciples, they returned to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27436AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27436AT\"></sup>Lystra and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27436AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27436AU\"></sup>Iconium and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27436AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27436AV\"></sup>Antioch,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>strengthening the souls of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27437AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27437AW\"></sup>the disciples, encouraging them to continue in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27437AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27437AX\"></sup>the faith, and <i>saying</i>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27437AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27437AY\"></sup>Through many tribulations we must enter the kingdom of God.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27438AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27438AZ\"></sup>they had appointed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27438BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27438BA\"></sup>elders for them in every church, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27438BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27438BB\"></sup>prayed with fasting, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27438BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27438BC\"></sup>commended them to the Lord in whom they had believed.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>They passed through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27439BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27439BD\"></sup>Pisidia and came into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27439BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27439BE\"></sup>Pamphylia.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When they had spoken the word in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27440BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27440BF\"></sup>Perga, they went down to Attalia.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>From there they sailed to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27441BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27441BG\"></sup>Antioch, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27441BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27441BH\"></sup>which they had been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27441BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27441BI\"></sup>commended to the grace of God for the work that they had accomplished.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When they had arrived and gathered the church together, they <i>began</i> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27442BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27442BJ\"></sup>report all things that God had done with them and how He had opened a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27442BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27442BK\"></sup>door of faith to the Gentiles.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And they spent a long time with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27443BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27443BL\"></sup>the disciples."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27444A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27444A\"></sup>Some men came down from Judea and <i>began</i> teaching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27444B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27444B\"></sup>the brethren, “Unless you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27444C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27444C\"></sup>circumcised according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27444D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27444D\"></sup>the custom of Moses, you cannot be saved.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And when Paul and Barnabas had great dissension and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27445E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27445E\"></sup>debate with them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27445F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27445F\"></sup><i>the brethren</i> determined that Paul and Barnabas and some others of them should go up to Jerusalem to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27445G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27445G\"></sup>apostles and elders concerning this issue.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27446H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27446H\"></sup>sent on their way by the church, they were passing through both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27446I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27446I\"></sup>Phoenicia and Samaria, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27446J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27446J\"></sup>describing in detail the conversion of the Gentiles, and were bringing great joy to all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27446K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27446K\"></sup>the brethren.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When they arrived at Jerusalem, they were received by the church and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27447L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27447L\"></sup>the apostles and the elders, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27447M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27447M\"></sup>reported all that God had done with them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27448N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27448N\"></sup>the sect of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27448O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27448O\"></sup>Pharisees who had believed stood up, saying, “It is necessary to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27448P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27448P\"></sup>circumcise them and to direct them to observe the Law of Moses.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27449Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27449Q\"></sup>The apostles and the elders came together to look into this matter.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>After there had been much <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27450R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27450R\"></sup>debate, Peter stood up and said to them, “Brethren, you know that in the early days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27450S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27450S\"></sup>God made a choice among you, that by my mouth the Gentiles would hear the word of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27450T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27450T\"></sup>the gospel and believe.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27451U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27451U\"></sup>who knows the heart, testified to them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27451V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27451V\"></sup>giving them the Holy Spirit, just as He also did to us;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27452W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27452W\"></sup>He made no distinction between us and them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27452X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27452X\"></sup>cleansing their hearts by faith.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now therefore why do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27453Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27453Y\"></sup>put God to the test by placing upon the neck of the disciples a yoke which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27453Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27453Z\"></sup>neither our fathers nor we have been able to bear?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But we believe that we are saved through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27454AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27454AA\"></sup>the grace of the Lord Jesus, in the same way as they also are.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>All the people kept silent, and they were listening to Barnabas and Paul as they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27455AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27455AB\"></sup>relating what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27455AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27455AC\"></sup>signs and wonders God had done through them among the Gentiles.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>After they had stopped speaking, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27456AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27456AD\"></sup>James answered, saying, “Brethren, listen to me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27457AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27457AE\"></sup>Simeon has related how God first concerned Himself about taking from among the Gentiles a people for His name.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>With this the words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27458AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27458AF\"></sup>the Prophets agree, just as it is written,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27459AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27459AG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">After these things</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27459AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27459AH\"></sup>I will return,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And I will rebuild the</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">tabernacle of David which has fallen</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And I will rebuild its ruins</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And I will restore it</span>,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27460AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27460AI\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">So that the rest of</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">mankind may seek the Lord</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And all the Gentiles</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27460AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27460AJ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">who are called by My name</span>,’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27461AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27461AK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Says the Lord, who</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27461AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27461AL\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">makes these things known from long ago</span>.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27462AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27462AM\"></sup>my judgment that we do not trouble those who are turning to God from among the Gentiles,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>but that we write to them that they abstain from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27463AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27463AN\"></sup>things contaminated by idols and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27463AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27463AO\"></sup>fornication and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27463AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27463AP\"></sup>what is strangled and from blood.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27464AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27464AQ\"></sup>Moses from ancient generations has in every city those who preach him, since he is read in the synagogues every Sabbath.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then it seemed good to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27465AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27465AR\"></sup>the apostles and the elders, with the whole church, to choose men from among them to send to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27465AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27465AS\"></sup>Antioch with Paul and Barnabas—Judas called Barsabbas, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27465AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27465AT\"></sup>Silas, leading men among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27465AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27465AU\"></sup>the brethren,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and they sent this letter by them,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27466AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27466AV\"></sup>The apostles and the brethren who are elders, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27466AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27466AW\"></sup>the brethren in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27466AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27466AX\"></sup>Antioch and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27466AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27466AY\"></sup>Syria and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27466AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27466AZ\"></sup>Cilicia who are from the Gentiles, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27466BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27466BA\"></sup>greetings.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Since we have heard that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27467BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27467BB\"></sup>some of our number to whom we gave no instruction have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27467BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27467BC\"></sup>disturbed you with <i>their</i> words, unsettling your souls,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27468BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27468BD\"></sup>it seemed good to us, having become of one mind, to select men to send to you with our beloved Barnabas and Paul,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>men who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27469BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27469BE\"></sup>risked their lives for the name of our Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Therefore we have sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27470BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27470BF\"></sup>Judas and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27470BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27470BG\"></sup>Silas, who themselves will also report the same things by word <i>of mouth</i>.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27471BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27471BH\"></sup>it seemed good to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27471BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27471BI\"></sup>the Holy Spirit and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27471BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27471BJ\"></sup>us to lay upon you no greater burden than these essentials:",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>that you abstain from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27472BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27472BK\"></sup>things sacrificed to idols and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27472BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27472BL\"></sup>blood and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27472BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27472BM\"></sup>things strangled and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27472BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27472BN\"></sup>fornication; if you keep yourselves free from such things, you will do well. Farewell.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>So when they were sent away, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27473BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27473BO\"></sup>they went down to Antioch; and having gathered the congregation together, they delivered the letter.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>When they had read it, they rejoiced because of its encouragement.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27475BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27475BP\"></sup>Judas and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27475BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27475BQ\"></sup>Silas, also being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27475BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27475BR\"></sup>prophets themselves, encouraged and strengthened <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27475BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27475BS\"></sup>the brethren with a lengthy message.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>After they had spent time <i>there</i>, they were sent away from the brethren <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27476BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27476BT\"></sup>in peace to those who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27476BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27476BU\"></sup>sent them out.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>[But it seemed good to Silas to remain there.]",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27478BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27478BV\"></sup>Paul and Barnabas stayed in Antioch, teaching and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27478BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27478BW\"></sup>preaching with many others also, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27478BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27478BX\"></sup>the word of the Lord.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>After some days Paul said to Barnabas, “Let us return and visit the brethren in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27479BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27479BY\"></sup>every city in which we proclaimed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27479BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27479BZ\"></sup>the word of the Lord, <i>and see</i> how they are.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Barnabas wanted to take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27480CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27480CA\"></sup>John, called Mark, along with them also.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>But Paul kept insisting that they should not take him along who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27481CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27481CB\"></sup>deserted them in Pamphylia and had not gone with them to the work.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And there occurred such a sharp disagreement that they separated from one another, and Barnabas took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27482CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27482CC\"></sup>Mark with him and sailed away to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27482CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27482CD\"></sup>Cyprus.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>But Paul chose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27483CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27483CE\"></sup>Silas and left, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27483CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27483CF\"></sup>committed by the brethren to the grace of the Lord.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And he was traveling through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27484CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27484CG\"></sup>Syria and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27484CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27484CH\"></sup>Cilicia, strengthening the churches."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Paul came also to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27485A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27485A\"></sup>Derbe and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27485B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27485B\"></sup>Lystra. And a disciple was there, named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27485C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27485C\"></sup>Timothy, the son of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27485D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27485D\"></sup>Jewish woman who was a believer, but his father was a Greek,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and he was well spoken of by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27486E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27486E\"></sup>the brethren who were in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27486F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27486F\"></sup>Lystra and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27486G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27486G\"></sup>Iconium.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Paul wanted this man to go with him; and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27487H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27487H\"></sup>took him and circumcised him because of the Jews who were in those parts, for they all knew that his father was a Greek.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now while they were passing through the cities, they were delivering <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27488I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27488I\"></sup>the decrees which had been decided upon by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27488J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27488J\"></sup>the apostles and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27488K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27488K\"></sup>elders who were in Jerusalem, for them to observe.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27489L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27489L\"></sup>the churches were being strengthened in the faith, and were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27489M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27489M\"></sup>increasing in number daily.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They passed through the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27490N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27490N\"></sup>Phrygian and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27490O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27490O\"></sup>Galatian region, having been forbidden by the Holy Spirit to speak the word in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27490P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27490P\"></sup>Asia;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and after they came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27491Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27491Q\"></sup>Mysia, they were trying to go into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27491R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27491R\"></sup>Bithynia, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27491S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27491S\"></sup>Spirit of Jesus did not permit them;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and passing by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27492T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27492T\"></sup>Mysia, they came down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27492U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27492U\"></sup>Troas.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27493V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27493V\"></sup>A vision appeared to Paul in the night: a man of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27493W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27493W\"></sup>Macedonia was standing and appealing to him, and saying, “Come over to Macedonia and help us.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When he had seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27494X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27494X\"></sup>the vision, immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27494Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27494Y\"></sup>we sought to go into Macedonia, concluding that God had called us to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27494Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27494Z\"></sup>preach the gospel to them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So putting out to sea from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27495AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27495AA\"></sup>Troas, we ran <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27495AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27495AB\"></sup>a straight course to Samothrace, and on the day following to Neapolis;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and from there to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27496AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27496AC\"></sup>Philippi, which is a leading city of the district of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27496AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27496AD\"></sup>Macedonia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27496AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27496AE\"></sup>a <i>Roman</i> colony; and we were staying in this city for some days.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27497AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27497AF\"></sup>the Sabbath day we went outside the gate to a riverside, where we were supposing that there would be a place of prayer; and we sat down and began speaking to the women who had assembled.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>A woman named Lydia, from the city of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27498AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27498AG\"></sup>Thyatira, a seller of purple fabrics, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27498AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27498AH\"></sup>a worshiper of God, was listening; and the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27498AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27498AI\"></sup>opened her heart to respond to the things spoken by Paul.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And when she and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27499AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27499AJ\"></sup>her household had been baptized, she urged us, saying, “If you have judged me to be faithful to the Lord, come into my house and stay.” And she prevailed upon us.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>It happened that as we were going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27500AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27500AK\"></sup>the place of prayer, a slave-girl having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27500AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27500AL\"></sup>a spirit of divination met us, who was bringing her masters much profit by fortune-telling.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Following after Paul and us, she kept crying out, saying, “These men are bond-servants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27501AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27501AM\"></sup>the Most High God, who are proclaiming to you the way of salvation.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>She continued doing this for many days. But Paul was greatly annoyed, and turned and said to the spirit, “I command you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27502AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27502AN\"></sup>in the name of Jesus Christ to come out of her!” And it came out at that very moment.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But when her masters saw that their hope of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27503AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27503AO\"></sup>profit was gone, they seized <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27503AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27503AP\"></sup>Paul and Silas and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27503AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27503AQ\"></sup>dragged them into the market place before the authorities,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and when they had brought them to the chief magistrates, they said, “These men are throwing our city into confusion, being Jews,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27505AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27505AR\"></sup>are proclaiming customs which it is not lawful for us to accept or to observe, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27505AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27505AS\"></sup>Romans.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The crowd rose up together against them, and the chief magistrates tore their robes off them and proceeded to order <i>them</i> to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27506AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27506AT\"></sup>beaten with rods.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When they had struck them with many blows, they threw them into prison, commanding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27507AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27507AU\"></sup>the jailer to guard them securely;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and he, having received such a command, threw them into the inner prison and fastened their feet in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27508AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27508AV\"></sup>the stocks.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But about midnight <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27509AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27509AW\"></sup>Paul and Silas were praying and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27509AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27509AX\"></sup>singing hymns of praise to God, and the prisoners were listening to them;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and suddenly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27510AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27510AY\"></sup>there came a great earthquake, so that the foundations of the prison house were shaken; and immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27510AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27510AZ\"></sup>all the doors were opened and everyone’s <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27510BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27510BA\"></sup>chains were unfastened.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27511BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27511BB\"></sup>the jailer awoke and saw the prison doors opened, he drew his sword and was about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27511BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27511BC\"></sup>to kill himself, supposing that the prisoners had escaped.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But Paul cried out with a loud voice, saying, “Do not harm yourself, for we are all here!”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And he called for lights and rushed in, and trembling with fear he fell down before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27513BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27513BD\"></sup>Paul and Silas,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>and after he brought them out, he said, “Sirs, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27514BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27514BE\"></sup>what must I do to be saved?”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>They said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27515BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27515BF\"></sup>Believe in the Lord Jesus, and you will be saved, you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27515BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27515BG\"></sup>your household.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And they spoke the word of the Lord to him together with all who were in his house.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And he took them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27517BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27517BH\"></sup>that <i>very</i> hour of the night and washed their wounds, and immediately he was baptized, he and all his <i>household</i>.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And he brought them into his house and set food before them, and rejoiced greatly, having believed in God with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27518BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27518BI\"></sup>his whole household.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Now when day came, the chief magistrates sent their policemen, saying, “Release those men.”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27520BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27520BJ\"></sup>the jailer reported these words to Paul, <i>saying</i>, “The chief magistrates have sent to release you. Therefore come out now and go <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27520BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27520BK\"></sup>in peace.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But Paul said to them, “They have beaten us in public without trial, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27521BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27521BL\"></sup>men who are Romans, and have thrown us into prison; and now are they sending us away secretly? No indeed! But let them come themselves and bring us out.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>The policemen reported these words to the chief magistrates. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27522BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27522BM\"></sup>They were afraid when they heard that they were Romans,",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>and they came and appealed to them, and when they had brought them out, they kept begging them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27523BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27523BN\"></sup>to leave the city.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>They went out of the prison and entered <i>the house of</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27524BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27524BO\"></sup>Lydia, and when they saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27524BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27524BP\"></sup>the brethren, they encouraged them and departed."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>Now when they had traveled through Amphipolis and Apollonia, they came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27525A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27525A\"></sup>Thessalonica, where there was a synagogue of the Jews.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27526B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27526B\"></sup>according to Paul’s custom, he went to them, and for three <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27526C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27526C\"></sup>Sabbaths reasoned with them from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27526D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27526D\"></sup>the Scriptures,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>explaining and giving evidence that the Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27527E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27527E\"></sup>had to suffer and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27527F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27527F\"></sup>rise again from the dead, and <i>saying</i>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27527G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27527G\"></sup>This Jesus whom I am proclaiming to you is the Christ.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27528H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27528H\"></sup>And some of them were persuaded and joined <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27528I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27528I\"></sup>Paul and Silas, along with a large number of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27528J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27528J\"></sup>God-fearing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27528K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27528K\"></sup>Greeks and a number of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27528L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27528L\"></sup>leading women.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27529M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27529M\"></sup>the Jews, becoming jealous and taking along some wicked men from the market place, formed a mob and set the city in an uproar; and attacking the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27529N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27529N\"></sup>Jason, they were seeking to bring them out to the people.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When they did not find them, they <i>began</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27530O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27530O\"></sup>dragging Jason and some brethren before the city authorities, shouting, “These men who have upset <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27530P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27530P\"></sup>the world have come here also;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and Jason <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27531Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27531Q\"></sup>has welcomed them, and they all act <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27531R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27531R\"></sup>contrary to the decrees of Caesar, saying that there is another king, Jesus.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They stirred up the crowd and the city authorities who heard these things.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And when they had received a pledge from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27533S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27533S\"></sup>Jason and the others, they released them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27534T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27534T\"></sup>The brethren immediately sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27534U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27534U\"></sup>Paul and Silas away by night to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27534V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27534V\"></sup>Berea, and when they arrived, they went into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27534W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27534W\"></sup>the synagogue of the Jews.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now these were more noble-minded than those in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27535X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27535X\"></sup>Thessalonica, for they received the word with great eagerness, examining the Scriptures daily <i>to see</i> whether these things were so.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27536Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27536Y\"></sup>many of them believed, along with a number of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27536Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27536Z\"></sup>prominent Greek <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27536AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27536AA\"></sup>women and men.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But when the Jews of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27537AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27537AB\"></sup>Thessalonica found out that the word of God had been proclaimed by Paul in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27537AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27537AC\"></sup>Berea also, they came there as well, agitating and stirring up the crowds.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27538AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27538AD\"></sup>the brethren sent Paul out to go as far as the sea; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27538AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27538AE\"></sup>Silas and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27538AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27538AF\"></sup>Timothy remained there.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27539AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27539AG\"></sup>those who escorted Paul brought him as far as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27539AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27539AH\"></sup>Athens; and receiving a command for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27539AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27539AI\"></sup>Silas and Timothy to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27539AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27539AJ\"></sup>come to him as soon as possible, they left.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now while Paul was waiting for them at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27540AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27540AK\"></sup>Athens, his spirit was being provoked within him as he was observing the city full of idols.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So he was reasoning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27541AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27541AL\"></sup>in the synagogue with the Jews and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27541AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27541AM\"></sup>the God-fearing <i>Gentiles</i>, and in the market place every day with those who happened to be present.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And also some of the Epicurean and Stoic philosophers were conversing with him. Some were saying, “What would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27542AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27542AN\"></sup>this idle babbler wish to say?” Others, “He seems to be a proclaimer of strange deities,”—because he was preaching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27542AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27542AO\"></sup>Jesus and the resurrection.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27543AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27543AP\"></sup>took him and brought him to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27543AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27543AQ\"></sup>Areopagus, saying, “May we know what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27543AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27543AR\"></sup>this new teaching is which you are proclaiming?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For you are bringing some strange things to our ears; so we want to know what these things mean.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>(Now all the Athenians and the strangers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27545AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27545AS\"></sup>visiting there used to spend their time in nothing other than telling or hearing something new.)",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So Paul stood in the midst of the Areopagus and said, “Men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27546AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27546AT\"></sup>Athens, I observe that you are very <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27546AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27546AU\"></sup>religious in all respects.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For while I was passing through and examining the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27547AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27547AV\"></sup>objects of your worship, I also found an altar with this inscription, ‘TO AN UNKNOWN GOD.’ Therefore what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27547AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27547AW\"></sup>you worship in ignorance, this I proclaim to you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27548AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27548AX\"></sup>The God who made the world and all things in it, since He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27548AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27548AY\"></sup>Lord of heaven and earth, does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27548AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27548AZ\"></sup>dwell in temples made with hands;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>nor is He served by human hands, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27549BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27549BA\"></sup>as though He needed anything, since He Himself gives to all <i>people</i> life and breath and all things;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27550BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27550BB\"></sup>He made from one <i>man</i> every nation of mankind to live on all the face of the earth, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27550BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27550BC\"></sup>determined <i>their</i> appointed times and the boundaries of their habitation,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>that they would seek God, if perhaps they might grope for Him and find Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27551BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27551BD\"></sup>though He is not far from each one of us;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27552BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27552BE\"></sup>in Him we live and move and exist, as even some of your own poets have said, ‘For we also are His children.’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Being then the children of God, we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27553BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27553BF\"></sup>ought not to think that the Divine Nature is like gold or silver or stone, an image formed by the art and thought of man.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Therefore having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27554BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27554BG\"></sup>overlooked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27554BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27554BH\"></sup>the times of ignorance, God is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27554BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27554BI\"></sup>now declaring to men that all <i>people</i> everywhere should repent,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>because He has fixed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27555BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27555BJ\"></sup>a day in which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27555BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27555BK\"></sup>He will judge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27555BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27555BL\"></sup>the world in righteousness through a Man whom He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27555BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27555BM\"></sup>appointed, having furnished proof to all men by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27555BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27555BN\"></sup>raising Him from the dead.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Now when they heard of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27556BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27556BO\"></sup>the resurrection of the dead, some <i>began</i> to sneer, but others said, “We shall hear you again concerning this.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So Paul went out of their midst.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But some men joined him and believed, among whom also were Dionysius the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27558BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27558BP\"></sup>Areopagite and a woman named Damaris and others with them."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>After these things he left <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27559A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27559A\"></sup>Athens and went to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27559B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27559B\"></sup>Corinth.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he found a Jew named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27560C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27560C\"></sup>Aquila, a native of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27560D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27560D\"></sup>Pontus, having recently come from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27560E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27560E\"></sup>Italy with his wife <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27560F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27560F\"></sup>Priscilla, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27560G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27560G\"></sup>Claudius had commanded all the Jews to leave Rome. He came to them,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and because he was of the same trade, he stayed with them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27561H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27561H\"></sup>they were working, for by trade they were tent-makers.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And he was reasoning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27562I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27562I\"></sup>in the synagogue every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27562J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27562J\"></sup>Sabbath and trying to persuade <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27562K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27562K\"></sup>Jews and Greeks.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27563L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27563L\"></sup>Silas and Timothy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27563M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27563M\"></sup>came down from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27563N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27563N\"></sup>Macedonia, Paul <i>began</i> devoting himself completely to the word, solemnly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27563O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27563O\"></sup>testifying to the Jews that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27563P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27563P\"></sup>Jesus was the Christ.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But when they resisted and blasphemed, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27564Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27564Q\"></sup>shook out his garments and said to them, “Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27564R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27564R\"></sup>blood <i>be</i> on your own heads! I am clean. From now on I will go <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27564S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27564S\"></sup>to the Gentiles.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then he left there and went to the house of a man named Titius Justus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27565T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27565T\"></sup>a worshiper of God, whose house was next to the synagogue.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27566U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27566U\"></sup>Crispus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27566V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27566V\"></sup>the leader of the synagogue, believed in the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27566W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27566W\"></sup>with all his household, and many of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27566X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27566X\"></sup>Corinthians when they heard were believing and being baptized.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the Lord said to Paul in the night by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27567Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27567Y\"></sup>a vision, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not be afraid <i>any longer</i>, but go on speaking and do not be silent;</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for I am with you, and no man will attack you in order to harm you, for I have many people in this city.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And he settled <i>there</i> a year and six months, teaching the word of God among them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But while Gallio was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27570Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27570Z\"></sup>proconsul of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27570AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27570AA\"></sup>Achaia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27570AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27570AB\"></sup>the Jews with one accord rose up against Paul and brought him before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27570AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27570AC\"></sup>the judgment seat,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>saying, “This man persuades men to worship God contrary to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27571AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27571AD\"></sup>the law.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But when Paul was about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27572AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27572AE\"></sup>open his mouth, Gallio said to the Jews, “If it were a matter of wrong or of vicious crime, O Jews, it would be reasonable for me to put up with you;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>but if there are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27573AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27573AF\"></sup>questions about words and names and your own law, look after it yourselves; I am unwilling to be a judge of these matters.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And he drove them away from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27574AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27574AG\"></sup>the judgment seat.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And they all took hold of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27575AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27575AH\"></sup>Sosthenes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27575AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27575AI\"></sup>the leader of the synagogue, and <i>began</i> beating him in front of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27575AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27575AJ\"></sup>the judgment seat. But Gallio was not concerned about any of these things.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Paul, having remained many days longer, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27576AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27576AK\"></sup>took leave of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27576AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27576AL\"></sup>the brethren and put out to sea for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27576AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27576AM\"></sup>Syria, and with him were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27576AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27576AN\"></sup>Priscilla and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27576AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27576AO\"></sup>Aquila. In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27576AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27576AP\"></sup>Cenchrea he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27576AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27576AQ\"></sup>had his hair cut, for he was keeping a vow.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27577AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27577AR\"></sup>Ephesus, and he left them there. Now he himself entered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27577AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27577AS\"></sup>the synagogue and reasoned with the Jews.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>When they asked him to stay for a longer time, he did not consent,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27579AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27579AT\"></sup>taking leave of them and saying, “I will return to you again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27579AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27579AU\"></sup>if God wills,” he set sail from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27579AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27579AV\"></sup>Ephesus.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>When he had landed at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27580AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27580AW\"></sup>Caesarea, he went up and greeted the church, and went down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27580AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27580AX\"></sup>Antioch.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And having spent some time <i>there</i>, he left and passed successively through the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27581AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27581AY\"></sup>Galatian region and Phrygia, strengthening all the disciples.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now a Jew named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27582AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27582AZ\"></sup>Apollos, an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27582BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27582BA\"></sup>Alexandrian by birth, an eloquent man, came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27582BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27582BB\"></sup>Ephesus; and he was mighty in the Scriptures.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>This man had been instructed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27583BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27583BC\"></sup>the way of the Lord; and being fervent in spirit, he was speaking and teaching accurately the things concerning Jesus, being acquainted only with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27583BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27583BD\"></sup>the baptism of John;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and he began to speak out boldly in the synagogue. But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27584BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27584BE\"></sup>Priscilla and Aquila heard him, they took him aside and explained to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27584BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27584BF\"></sup>the way of God more accurately.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And when he wanted to go across to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27585BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27585BG\"></sup>Achaia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27585BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27585BH\"></sup>the brethren encouraged him and wrote to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27585BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27585BI\"></sup>the disciples to welcome him; and when he had arrived, he greatly helped those who had believed through grace,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>for he powerfully refuted the Jews in public, demonstrating <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27586BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27586BJ\"></sup>by the Scriptures that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27586BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27586BK\"></sup>Jesus was the Christ."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>It happened that while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27587A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27587A\"></sup>Apollos was at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27587B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27587B\"></sup>Corinth, Paul passed through the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27587C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27587C\"></sup>upper country and came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27587D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27587D\"></sup>Ephesus, and found some disciples.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He said to them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27588E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27588E\"></sup>Did you receive the Holy Spirit when you believed?” And they <i>said</i> to him, “No, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27588F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27588F\"></sup>we have not even heard whether there is a Holy Spirit.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And he said, “Into what then were you baptized?” And they said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27589G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27589G\"></sup>Into John’s baptism.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Paul said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27590H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27590H\"></sup>John baptized with the baptism of repentance, telling the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27590I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27590I\"></sup>to believe in Him who was coming after him, that is, in Jesus.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When they heard this, they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27591J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27591J\"></sup>baptized in the name of the Lord Jesus.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And when Paul had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27592K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27592K\"></sup>laid his hands upon them, the Holy Spirit came on them, and they <i>began</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27592L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27592L\"></sup>speaking with tongues and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27592M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27592M\"></sup>prophesying.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There were in all about twelve men.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And he entered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27594N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27594N\"></sup>the synagogue and continued speaking out boldly for three months, reasoning and persuading <i>them</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27594O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27594O\"></sup>about the kingdom of God.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27595P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27595P\"></sup>some were becoming hardened and disobedient, speaking evil of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27595Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27595Q\"></sup>the Way before the people, he withdrew from them and took away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27595R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27595R\"></sup>the disciples, reasoning daily in the school of Tyrannus.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This took place for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27596S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27596S\"></sup>two years, so that all who lived in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27596T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27596T\"></sup>Asia heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27596U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27596U\"></sup>the word of the Lord, both Jews and Greeks.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>God was performing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27597V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27597V\"></sup>extraordinary miracles by the hands of Paul,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27598W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27598W\"></sup>so that handkerchiefs or aprons were even carried from his body to the sick, and the diseases left them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27598X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27598X\"></sup>the evil spirits went out.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But also some of the Jewish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27599Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27599Y\"></sup>exorcists, who went from place to place, attempted to name over those who had the evil spirits the name of the Lord Jesus, saying, “I adjure you by Jesus whom Paul preaches.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Seven sons of one Sceva, a Jewish chief priest, were doing this.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the evil spirit answered and said to them, “I recognize Jesus, and I know about Paul, but who are you?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And the man, in whom was the evil spirit, leaped on them and subdued all of them and overpowered them, so that they fled out of that house naked and wounded.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>This became known to all, both Jews and Greeks, who lived in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27603Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27603Z\"></sup>Ephesus; and fear fell upon them all and the name of the Lord Jesus was being magnified.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Many also of those who had believed kept coming, confessing and disclosing their practices.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And many of those who practiced magic brought their books together and <i>began</i> burning them in the sight of everyone; and they counted up the price of them and found it fifty thousand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27605AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27605AA\"></sup>pieces of silver.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27606AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27606AB\"></sup>the word of the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27606AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27606AC\"></sup>was growing mightily and prevailing.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Now after these things were finished, Paul purposed in the Spirit to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27607AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27607AD\"></sup>go to Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27607AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27607AE\"></sup>after he had passed through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27607AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27607AF\"></sup>Macedonia and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27607AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27607AG\"></sup>Achaia, saying, “After I have been there, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27607AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27607AH\"></sup>I must also see Rome.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And having sent into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27608AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27608AI\"></sup>Macedonia two of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27608AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27608AJ\"></sup>those who ministered to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27608AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27608AK\"></sup>Timothy and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27608AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27608AL\"></sup>Erastus, he himself stayed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27608AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27608AM\"></sup>Asia for a while.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>About that time there occurred no small disturbance concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27609AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27609AN\"></sup>the Way.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For a man named Demetrius, a silversmith, who made silver shrines of Artemis, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27610AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27610AO\"></sup>was bringing no little business to the craftsmen;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>these he gathered together with the workmen of similar <i>trades</i>, and said, “Men, you know that our prosperity depends upon this business.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>You see and hear that not only in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27612AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27612AP\"></sup>Ephesus, but in almost all of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27612AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27612AQ\"></sup>Asia, this Paul has persuaded and turned away a considerable number of people, saying that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27612AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27612AR\"></sup>gods made with hands are no gods <i>at all</i>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Not only is there danger that this trade of ours fall into disrepute, but also that the temple of the great goddess Artemis be regarded as worthless and that she whom all of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27613AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27613AS\"></sup>Asia and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27613AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27613AT\"></sup>the world worship will even be dethroned from her magnificence.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When they heard <i>this</i> and were filled with rage, they <i>began</i> crying out, saying, “Great is Artemis of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27614AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27614AU\"></sup>Ephesians!”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The city was filled with the confusion, and they rushed with one accord into the theater, dragging along <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27615AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27615AV\"></sup>Gaius and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27615AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27615AW\"></sup>Aristarchus, Paul’s traveling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27615AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27615AX\"></sup>companions from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27615AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27615AY\"></sup>Macedonia.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And when Paul wanted to go into the assembly, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27616AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27616AZ\"></sup>the disciples would not let him.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Also some of the Asiarchs who were friends of his sent to him and repeatedly urged him not to venture into the theater.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27618BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27618BA\"></sup>So then, some were shouting one thing and some another, for the assembly was in confusion and the majority did not know for what reason they had come together.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Some of the crowd concluded <i>it was</i> Alexander, since the Jews had put him forward; and having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27619BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27619BB\"></sup>motioned with his hand, Alexander was intending to make a defense to the assembly.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But when they recognized that he was a Jew, a <i>single</i> outcry arose from them all as they shouted for about two hours, “Great is Artemis of the Ephesians!”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>After quieting the crowd, the town clerk *said, “Men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27621BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27621BC\"></sup>Ephesus, what man is there after all who does not know that the city of the Ephesians is guardian of the temple of the great Artemis and of the <i>image</i> which fell down from heaven?",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>So, since these are undeniable facts, you ought to keep calm and to do nothing rash.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For you have brought these men <i>here</i> who are neither <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27623BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27623BD\"></sup>robbers of temples nor blasphemers of our goddess.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>So then, if Demetrius and the craftsmen who are with him have a complaint against any man, the courts are in session and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27624BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27624BE\"></sup>proconsuls are <i>available</i>; let them bring charges against one another.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But if you want anything beyond this, it shall be settled in the lawful assembly.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>For indeed we are in danger of being accused of a riot in connection with today’s events, since there is no <i>real</i> cause <i>for it</i>, and in this connection we will be unable to account for this disorderly gathering.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>After saying this he dismissed the assembly."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>After the uproar had ceased, Paul sent for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27628A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27628A\"></sup>the disciples, and when he had exhorted them and taken his leave of them, he left <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27628B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27628B\"></sup>to go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27628C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27628C\"></sup>Macedonia.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When he had gone through those districts and had given them much exhortation, he came to Greece.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <i>there</i> he spent three months, and when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27630D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27630D\"></sup>a plot was formed against him by the Jews as he was about to set sail for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27630E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27630E\"></sup>Syria, he decided to return through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27630F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27630F\"></sup>Macedonia.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And he was accompanied by Sopater of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27631G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27631G\"></sup>Berea, <i>the son</i> of Pyrrhus, and by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27631H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27631H\"></sup>Aristarchus and Secundus of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27631I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27631I\"></sup>Thessalonians, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27631J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27631J\"></sup>Gaius of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27631K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27631K\"></sup>Derbe, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27631L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27631L\"></sup>Timothy, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27631M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27631M\"></sup>Tychicus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27631N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27631N\"></sup>Trophimus of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27631O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27631O\"></sup>Asia.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But these had gone on ahead and were waiting for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27632P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27632P\"></sup>us at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27632Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27632Q\"></sup>Troas.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27633R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27633R\"></sup>We sailed from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27633S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27633S\"></sup>Philippi after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27633T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27633T\"></sup>the days of Unleavened Bread, and came to them at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27633U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27633U\"></sup>Troas within five days; and there we stayed seven days.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>On <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27634V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27634V\"></sup>the first day of the week, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27634W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27634W\"></sup>we were gathered together to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27634X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27634X\"></sup>break bread, Paul <i>began</i> talking to them, intending to leave the next day, and he prolonged his message until midnight.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>There were many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27635Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27635Y\"></sup>lamps in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27635Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27635Z\"></sup>upper room where we were gathered together.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And there was a young man named Eutychus sitting on the window sill, sinking into a deep sleep; and as Paul kept on talking, he was overcome by sleep and fell down from the third floor and was picked up dead.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But Paul went down and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27637AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27637AA\"></sup>fell upon him, and after embracing him, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27637AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27637AB\"></sup>said, “Do not be troubled, for his life is in him.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When he had gone <i>back</i> up and had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27638AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27638AC\"></sup>broken the bread and eaten, he talked with them a long while until daybreak, and then left.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They took away the boy alive, and were greatly comforted.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27640AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27640AD\"></sup>we, going ahead to the ship, set sail for Assos, intending from there to take Paul on board; for so he had arranged it, intending himself to go by land.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And when he met us at Assos, we took him on board and came to Mitylene.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Sailing from there, we arrived the following day opposite Chios; and the next day we crossed over to Samos; and the day following we came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27642AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27642AE\"></sup>Miletus.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For Paul had decided to sail past <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27643AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27643AF\"></sup>Ephesus so that he would not have to spend time in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27643AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27643AG\"></sup>Asia; for he was hurrying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27643AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27643AH\"></sup>to be in Jerusalem, if possible, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27643AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27643AI\"></sup>on the day of Pentecost.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>From Miletus he sent to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27644AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27644AJ\"></sup>Ephesus and called to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27644AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27644AK\"></sup>the elders of the church.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And when they had come to him, he said to them,“You yourselves know, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27645AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27645AL\"></sup>from the first day that I set foot in Asia, how I was with you the whole time,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>serving the Lord with all humility and with tears and with trials which came upon me through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27646AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27646AM\"></sup>the plots of the Jews;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>how I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27647AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27647AN\"></sup>did not shrink from declaring to you anything that was profitable, and teaching you publicly and from house to house,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>solemnly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27648AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27648AO\"></sup>testifying to both Jews and Greeks of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27648AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27648AP\"></sup>repentance toward God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27648AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27648AQ\"></sup>faith in our Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And now, behold, bound by the Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27649AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27649AR\"></sup>I am on my way to Jerusalem, not knowing what will happen to me there,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>except that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27650AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27650AS\"></sup>the Holy Spirit solemnly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27650AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27650AT\"></sup>testifies to me in every city, saying that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27650AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27650AU\"></sup>bonds and afflictions await me.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27651AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27651AV\"></sup>I do not consider my life of any account as dear to myself, so that I may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27651AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27651AW\"></sup>finish my course and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27651AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27651AX\"></sup>the ministry which I received from the Lord Jesus, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27651AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27651AY\"></sup>testify solemnly of the gospel of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27651AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27651AZ\"></sup>the grace of God.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“And now, behold, I know that all of you, among whom I went about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27652BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27652BA\"></sup>preaching the kingdom, will no longer see my face.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Therefore, I testify to you this day that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27653BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27653BB\"></sup>I am innocent of the blood of all men.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27654BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27654BC\"></sup>did not shrink from declaring to you the whole <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27654BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27654BD\"></sup>purpose of God.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Be on guard for yourselves and for all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27655BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27655BE\"></sup>the flock, among which the Holy Spirit has made you overseers, to shepherd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27655BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27655BF\"></sup>the church of God which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27655BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27655BG\"></sup>He purchased with His own blood.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I know that after my departure <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27656BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27656BH\"></sup>savage wolves will come in among you, not sparing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27656BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27656BI\"></sup>the flock;",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>and from among your own selves men will arise, speaking perverse things, to draw away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27657BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27657BJ\"></sup>the disciples after them.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Therefore be on the alert, remembering that night and day for a period of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27658BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27658BK\"></sup>three years I did not cease to admonish each one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27658BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27658BL\"></sup>with tears.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And now I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27659BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27659BM\"></sup>commend you to God and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27659BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27659BN\"></sup>the word of His grace, which is able to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27659BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27659BO\"></sup>build <i>you</i> up and to give <i>you</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27659BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27659BP\"></sup>the inheritance among all those who are sanctified.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27660BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27660BQ\"></sup>I have coveted no one’s silver or gold or clothes.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>You yourselves know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27661BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27661BR\"></sup>these hands ministered to my <i>own</i> needs and to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27661BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27661BS\"></sup>men who were with me.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>In everything I showed you that by working hard in this manner you must help the weak and remember the words of the Lord Jesus, that He Himself said, <span class=\"woj\">‘It is more blessed to give than to receive.’</span>”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>When he had said these things, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27663BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27663BT\"></sup>knelt down and prayed with them all.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And they <i>began</i> to weep aloud and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27664BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27664BU\"></sup>embraced Paul, and repeatedly kissed him,",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>grieving especially over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27665BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27665BV\"></sup>the word which he had spoken, that they would not see his face again. And they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27665BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27665BW\"></sup>accompanying him to the ship."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27666A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27666A\"></sup>we had parted from them and had set sail, we ran <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27666B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27666B\"></sup>a straight course to Cos and the next day to Rhodes and from there to Patara;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and having found a ship crossing over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27667C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27667C\"></sup>Phoenicia, we went aboard and set sail.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When we came in sight of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27668D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27668D\"></sup>Cyprus, leaving it on the left, we kept sailing to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27668E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27668E\"></sup>Syria and landed at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27668F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27668F\"></sup>Tyre; for there the ship was to unload its cargo.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>After looking up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27669G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27669G\"></sup>the disciples, we stayed there seven days; and they kept telling Paul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27669H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27669H\"></sup>through the Spirit not to set foot in Jerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When our days there were ended, we left and started on our journey, while they all, with wives and children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27670I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27670I\"></sup>escorted us until <i>we were</i> out of the city. After <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27670J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27670J\"></sup>kneeling down on the beach and praying, we said farewell to one another.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then we went on board the ship, and they returned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27671K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27671K\"></sup>home again.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When we had finished the voyage from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27672L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27672L\"></sup>Tyre, we arrived at Ptolemais, and after greeting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27672M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27672M\"></sup>the brethren, we stayed with them for a day.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>On the next day we left and came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27673N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27673N\"></sup>Caesarea, and entering the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27673O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27673O\"></sup>Philip the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27673P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27673P\"></sup>evangelist, who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27673Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27673Q\"></sup>one of the seven, we stayed with him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now this man had four virgin daughters who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27674R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27674R\"></sup>prophetesses.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>As we were staying there for some days, a prophet named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27675S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27675S\"></sup>Agabus came down from Judea.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And coming to us, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27676T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27676T\"></sup>took Paul’s belt and bound his own feet and hands, and said, “This <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27676U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27676U\"></sup>is what the Holy Spirit says: ‘In this way the Jews at Jerusalem will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27676V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27676V\"></sup>bind the man who owns this belt and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27676W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27676W\"></sup>deliver him into the hands of the Gentiles.’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When we had heard this, we as well as the local residents <i>began</i> begging him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27677X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27677X\"></sup>not to go up to Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then Paul answered, “What are you doing, weeping and breaking my heart? For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27678Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27678Y\"></sup>I am ready not only to be bound, but even to die at Jerusalem for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27678Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27678Z\"></sup>the name of the Lord Jesus.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And since he would not be persuaded, we fell silent, remarking, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27679AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27679AA\"></sup>The will of the Lord be done!”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>After these days we got ready and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27680AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27680AB\"></sup>started on our way up to Jerusalem.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><i>Some</i> of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27681AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27681AC\"></sup>the disciples from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27681AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27681AD\"></sup>Caesarea also came with us, taking us to Mnason of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27681AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27681AE\"></sup>Cyprus, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27681AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27681AF\"></sup>disciple of long standing with whom we were to lodge.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>After we arrived in Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27682AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27682AG\"></sup>the brethren received us gladly.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And the following day Paul went in with us to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27683AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27683AH\"></sup>James, and all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27683AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27683AI\"></sup>the elders were present.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>After he had greeted them, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27684AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27684AJ\"></sup><i>began</i> to relate one by one the things which God had done among the Gentiles through his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27684AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27684AK\"></sup>ministry.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And when they heard it they <i>began</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27685AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27685AL\"></sup>glorifying God; and they said to him, “You see, brother, how many thousands there are among the Jews of those who have believed, and they are all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27685AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27685AM\"></sup>zealous for the Law;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and they have been told about you, that you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27686AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27686AN\"></sup>teaching all the Jews who are among the Gentiles to forsake Moses, telling them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27686AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27686AO\"></sup>not to circumcise their children nor to walk according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27686AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27686AP\"></sup>the customs.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>What, then, is <i>to be done</i>? They will certainly hear that you have come.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Therefore do this that we tell you. We have four men who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27688AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27688AQ\"></sup>are under a vow;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>take them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27689AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27689AR\"></sup>purify yourself along with them, and pay their expenses so that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27689AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27689AS\"></sup>shave their heads; and all will know that there is nothing to the things which they have been told about you, but that you yourself also walk orderly, keeping the Law.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But concerning the Gentiles who have believed, we wrote, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27690AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27690AT\"></sup>having decided that they should abstain from meat sacrificed to idols and from blood and from what is strangled and from fornication.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then Paul took the men, and the next day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27691AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27691AU\"></sup>purifying himself along with them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27691AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27691AV\"></sup>went into the temple giving notice of the completion of the days of purification, until the sacrifice was offered for each one of them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27692AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27692AW\"></sup>the seven days were almost over, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27692AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27692AX\"></sup>the Jews from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27692AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27692AY\"></sup>Asia, upon seeing him in the temple, <i>began</i> to stir up all the crowd and laid hands on him,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>crying out, “Men of Israel, come to our aid! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27693AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27693AZ\"></sup>This is the man who preaches to all men everywhere against our people and the Law and this place; and besides he has even brought Greeks into the temple and has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27693BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27693BA\"></sup>defiled this holy place.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For they had previously seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27694BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27694BB\"></sup>Trophimus the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27694BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27694BC\"></sup>Ephesian in the city with him, and they supposed that Paul had brought him into the temple.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Then all the city was provoked, and the people rushed together, and taking hold of Paul they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27695BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27695BD\"></sup>dragged him out of the temple, and immediately the doors were shut.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>While they were seeking to kill him, a report came up to the commander of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27696BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27696BE\"></sup><i>Roman</i> cohort that all Jerusalem was in confusion.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>At once he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27697BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27697BF\"></sup>took along <i>some</i> soldiers and centurions and ran down to them; and when they saw the commander and the soldiers, they stopped beating Paul.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Then the commander came up and took hold of him, and ordered him to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27698BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27698BG\"></sup>bound with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27698BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27698BH\"></sup>two chains; and he <i>began</i> asking who he was and what he had done.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But among the crowd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27699BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27699BI\"></sup>some were shouting one thing <i>and</i> some another, and when he could not find out the facts because of the uproar, he ordered him to be brought into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27699BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27699BJ\"></sup>the barracks.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>When he got to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27700BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27700BK\"></sup>the stairs, he was carried by the soldiers because of the violence of the mob;",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>for the multitude of the people kept following them, shouting, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27701BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27701BL\"></sup>Away with him!”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>As Paul was about to be brought into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27702BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27702BM\"></sup>the barracks, he said to the commander, “May I say something to you?” And he *said, “Do you know Greek?",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Then you are not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27703BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27703BN\"></sup>the Egyptian who some time ago stirred up a revolt and led the four thousand men of the Assassins out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27703BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27703BO\"></sup>into the wilderness?”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But Paul said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27704BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27704BP\"></sup>I am a Jew of Tarsus in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27704BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27704BQ\"></sup>Cilicia, a citizen of no insignificant city; and I beg you, allow me to speak to the people.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>When he had given him permission, Paul, standing on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27705BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27705BR\"></sup>the stairs, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27705BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27705BS\"></sup>motioned to the people with his hand; and when there was a great hush, he spoke to them in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27705BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27705BT\"></sup>Hebrew dialect, saying,"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27706A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27706A\"></sup>Brethren and fathers, hear my defense which I now <i>offer</i> to you.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And when they heard that he was addressing them in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27707B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27707B\"></sup>Hebrew dialect, they became even more quiet; and he *said,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27708C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27708C\"></sup>I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27708D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27708D\"></sup>a Jew, born in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27708E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27708E\"></sup>Tarsus of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27708F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27708F\"></sup>Cilicia, but brought up in this city, educated under <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27708G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27708G\"></sup>Gamaliel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27708H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27708H\"></sup>strictly according to the law of our fathers, being zealous for God just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27708I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27708I\"></sup>you all are today.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27709J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27709J\"></sup>I persecuted this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27709K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27709K\"></sup>Way to the death, binding and putting both men and women into prisons,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>as also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27710L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27710L\"></sup>the high priest and all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27710M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27710M\"></sup>the Council of the elders can testify. From them I also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27710N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27710N\"></sup>received letters to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27710O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27710O\"></sup>the brethren, and started off for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27710P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27710P\"></sup>Damascus in order to bring even those who were there to Jerusalem as prisoners to be punished.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27711Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27711Q\"></sup>But it happened that as I was on my way, approaching Damascus about noontime, a very bright light suddenly flashed from heaven all around me,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and I fell to the ground and heard a voice saying to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘Saul, Saul, why are you persecuting Me?’</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And I answered, ‘Who are You, Lord?’ And He said to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27713R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27713R\"></sup>Jesus the Nazarene, whom you are persecuting.’</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And those who were with me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27714S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27714S\"></sup>saw the light, to be sure, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27714T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27714T\"></sup>did not understand the voice of the One who was speaking to me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And I said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27715U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27715U\"></sup>What shall I do, Lord?’ And the Lord said to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘Get up and go on into Damascus, and there you will be told of all that has been appointed for you to do.’</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But since I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27716V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27716V\"></sup>could not see because of the brightness of that light, I was led by the hand by those who were with me and came into Damascus.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“A certain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27717W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27717W\"></sup>Ananias, a man who was devout by the standard of the Law, <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27717X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27717X\"></sup>well spoken of by all the Jews who lived there,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>came to me, and standing near said to me, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27718Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27718Y\"></sup>Brother Saul, receive your sight!’ And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27718Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27718Z\"></sup>at that very time I looked up at him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And he said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27719AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27719AA\"></sup>The God of our fathers has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27719AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27719AB\"></sup>appointed you to know His will and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27719AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27719AC\"></sup>see the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27719AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27719AD\"></sup>Righteous One and to hear an utterance from His mouth.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27720AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27720AE\"></sup>a witness for Him to all men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27720AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27720AF\"></sup>what you have seen and heard.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now why do you delay? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27721AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27721AG\"></sup>Get up and be baptized, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27721AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27721AH\"></sup>wash away your sins, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27721AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27721AI\"></sup>calling on His name.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“It happened when I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27722AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27722AJ\"></sup>returned to Jerusalem and was praying in the temple, that I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27722AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27722AK\"></sup>fell into a trance,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and I saw Him saying to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27723AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27723AL\"></sup>Make haste, and get out of Jerusalem quickly, because they will not accept your testimony about Me.’</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And I said, ‘Lord, they themselves understand that in one synagogue after another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27724AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27724AM\"></sup>I used to imprison and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27724AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27724AN\"></sup>beat those who believed in You.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27725AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27725AO\"></sup>when the blood of Your witness Stephen was being shed, I also was standing by approving, and watching out for the coats of those who were slaying him.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And He said to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘Go! For I will send you far away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27726AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27726AP\"></sup>to the Gentiles.’</span>”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>They listened to him up to this statement, and <i>then</i> they raised their voices and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27727AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27727AQ\"></sup>Away with such a fellow from the earth, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27727AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27727AR\"></sup>he should not be allowed to live!”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And as they were crying out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27728AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27728AS\"></sup>throwing off their cloaks and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27728AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27728AT\"></sup>tossing dust into the air,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>the commander ordered him to be brought into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27729AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27729AU\"></sup>the barracks, stating that he should be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27729AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27729AV\"></sup>examined by scourging so that he might find out the reason why they were shouting against him that way.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But when they stretched him out with thongs, Paul said to the centurion who was standing by, “Is it lawful for you to scourge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27730AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27730AW\"></sup>a man who is a Roman and uncondemned?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>When the centurion heard <i>this</i>, he went to the commander and told him, saying, “What are you about to do? For this man is a Roman.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The commander came and said to him, “Tell me, are you a Roman?” And he said, “Yes.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The commander answered, “I acquired this citizenship with a large sum of money.” And Paul said, “But I was actually born <i>a citizen</i>.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Therefore those who were about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27734AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27734AX\"></sup>examine him immediately let go of him; and the commander also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27734AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27734AY\"></sup>was afraid when he found out that he was a Roman, and because he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27734AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27734AZ\"></sup>put him in chains.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But on the next day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27735BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27735BA\"></sup>wishing to know for certain why he had been accused by the Jews, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27735BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27735BB\"></sup>released him and ordered the chief priests and all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27735BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27735BC\"></sup>the Council to assemble, and brought Paul down and set him before them."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>Paul, looking intently at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27736A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27736A\"></sup>the Council, said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27736B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27736B\"></sup>Brethren, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27736C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27736C\"></sup>I have lived my life with a perfectly good conscience before God up to this day.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27737D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27737D\"></sup>Ananias commanded those standing beside him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27737E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27737E\"></sup>to strike him on the mouth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then Paul said to him, “God is going to strike you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27738F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27738F\"></sup>you whitewashed wall! Do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27738G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27738G\"></sup>sit to try me according to the Law, and in violation of the Law order me to be struck?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But the bystanders said, “Do you revile God’s high priest?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And Paul said, “I was not aware, brethren, that he was high priest; for it is written, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27740H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27740H\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall not speak evil of a ruler of your people</span>.’”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But perceiving that one group were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27741I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27741I\"></sup>Sadducees and the other Pharisees, Paul <i>began</i> crying out in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27741J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27741J\"></sup>the Council, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27741K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27741K\"></sup>Brethren, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27741L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27741L\"></sup>I am a Pharisee, a son of Pharisees; I am on trial for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27741M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27741M\"></sup>the hope and resurrection of the dead!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>As he said this, there occurred a dissension between the Pharisees and Sadducees, and the assembly was divided.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27743N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27743N\"></sup>the Sadducees say that there is no resurrection, nor an angel, nor a spirit, but the Pharisees acknowledge them all.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And there occurred a great uproar; and some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27744O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27744O\"></sup>the scribes of the Pharisaic party stood up and <i>began</i> to argue heatedly, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27744P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27744P\"></sup>We find nothing wrong with this man; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27744Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27744Q\"></sup>suppose a spirit or an angel has spoken to him?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And as a great dissension was developing, the commander was afraid Paul would be torn to pieces by them and ordered the troops to go down and take him away from them by force, and bring him into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27745R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27745R\"></sup>the barracks.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27746S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27746S\"></sup>the night <i>immediately</i> following, the Lord stood at his side and said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27746T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27746T\"></sup>Take courage; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27746U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27746U\"></sup>as you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27746V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27746V\"></sup>solemnly witnessed to My cause at Jerusalem, so you must witness at Rome also.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When it was day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27747W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27747W\"></sup>the Jews formed a conspiracy and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27747X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27747X\"></sup>bound themselves under an oath, saying that they would neither eat nor drink until they had killed Paul.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>There were more than forty who formed this plot.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They came to the chief priests and the elders and said, “We have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27749Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27749Y\"></sup>bound ourselves under a solemn oath to taste nothing until we have killed Paul.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now therefore, you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27750Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27750Z\"></sup>the Council notify the commander to bring him down to you, as though you were going to determine his case by a more thorough investigation; and we for our part are ready to slay him before he comes near <i>the place</i>.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But the son of Paul’s sister heard of their ambush, and he came and entered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27751AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27751AA\"></sup>the barracks and told Paul.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Paul called one of the centurions to him and said, “Lead this young man to the commander, for he has something to report to him.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>So he took him and led him to the commander and *said, “Paul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27753AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27753AB\"></sup>the prisoner called me to him and asked me to lead this young man to you since he has something to tell you.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The commander took him by the hand and stepping aside, <i>began</i> to inquire of him privately, “What is it that you have to report to me?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And he said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27755AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27755AC\"></sup>The Jews have agreed to ask you to bring Paul down tomorrow to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27755AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27755AD\"></sup>the Council, as though they were going to inquire somewhat more thoroughly about him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So do not listen to them, for more than forty of them are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27756AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27756AE\"></sup>lying in wait for him who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27756AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27756AF\"></sup>bound themselves under a curse not to eat or drink until they slay him; and now they are ready and waiting for the promise from you.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So the commander let the young man go, instructing him, “Tell no one that you have notified me of these things.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And he called to him two of the centurions and said, “Get two hundred soldiers ready by the third hour of the night to proceed to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27758AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27758AG\"></sup>Caesarea, with seventy horsemen and two hundred spearmen.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><i>They were</i> also to provide mounts to put Paul on and bring him safely to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27759AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27759AH\"></sup>Felix the governor.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And he wrote a letter having this form:",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Claudius Lysias, to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27761AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27761AI\"></sup>most excellent governor Felix, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27761AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27761AJ\"></sup>greetings.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“When this man was arrested by the Jews and was about to be slain by them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27762AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27762AK\"></sup>I came up to them with the troops and rescued him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27762AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27762AL\"></sup>having learned that he was a Roman.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27763AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27763AM\"></sup>wanting to ascertain the charge for which they were accusing him, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27763AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27763AN\"></sup>brought him down to their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27763AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27763AO\"></sup>Council;",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>and I found him to be accused over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27764AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27764AP\"></sup>questions about their Law, but under <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27764AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27764AQ\"></sup>no accusation deserving death or imprisonment.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“When I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27765AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27765AR\"></sup>informed that there would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27765AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27765AS\"></sup>a plot against the man, I sent him to you at once, also instructing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27765AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27765AT\"></sup>his accusers to bring charges against him before you.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So the soldiers, in accordance with their orders, took Paul and brought him by night to Antipatris.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>But the next day, leaving <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27767AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27767AU\"></sup>the horsemen to go on with him, they returned to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27767AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27767AV\"></sup>the barracks.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>When these had come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27768AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27768AW\"></sup>Caesarea and delivered the letter to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27768AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27768AX\"></sup>the governor, they also presented Paul to him.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>When he had read it, he asked from what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27769AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27769AY\"></sup>province he was, and when he learned that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27769AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27769AZ\"></sup>he was from Cilicia,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>he said, “I will give you a hearing after your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27770BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27770BA\"></sup>accusers arrive also,” giving orders for him to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27770BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27770BB\"></sup>kept in Herod’s Praetorium."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>After <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27771A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27771A\"></sup>five days the high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27771B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27771B\"></sup>Ananias came down with some elders, with an attorney <i>named</i> Tertullus, and they brought charges to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27771C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27771C\"></sup>the governor against Paul.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>After <i>Paul</i> had been summoned, Tertullus began to accuse him, saying <i>to the governor</i>,“Since we have through you attained much peace, and since by your providence reforms are being carried out for this nation,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>we acknowledge <i>this</i> in every way and everywhere, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27773D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27773D\"></sup>most excellent Felix, with all thankfulness.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But, that I may not weary you any further, I beg you to grant us, by your kindness, a brief hearing.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For we have found this man a real pest and a fellow who stirs up dissension among all the Jews throughout the world, and a ringleader of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27775E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27775E\"></sup>sect of the Nazarenes.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And he even tried to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27776F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27776F\"></sup>desecrate the temple; and then we arrested him. [We wanted to judge him according to our own Law.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But Lysias the commander came along, and with much violence took him out of our hands,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>ordering his accusers to come before you.] By examining him yourself concerning all these matters you will be able to ascertain the things of which we accuse him.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27779G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27779G\"></sup>The Jews also joined in the attack, asserting that these things were so.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27780H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27780H\"></sup>the governor had nodded for him to speak, Paul responded:“Knowing that for many years you have been a judge to this nation, I cheerfully make my defense,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>since you can take note of the fact that no more than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27781I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27781I\"></sup>twelve days ago I went up to Jerusalem to worship.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27782J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27782J\"></sup>Neither in the temple, nor in the synagogues, nor in the city <i>itself</i> did they find me carrying on a discussion with anyone or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27782K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27782K\"></sup>causing a riot.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27783L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27783L\"></sup>Nor can they prove to you <i>the charges</i> of which they now accuse me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But this I admit to you, that according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27784M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27784M\"></sup>the Way which they call a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27784N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27784N\"></sup>sect I do serve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27784O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27784O\"></sup>the God of our fathers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27784P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27784P\"></sup>believing everything that is in accordance with the Law and that is written in the Prophets;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>having a hope in God, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27785Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27785Q\"></sup>these men cherish themselves, that there shall certainly be a resurrection of both the righteous and the wicked.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In view of this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27786R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27786R\"></sup>I also do my best to maintain always a blameless conscience <i>both</i> before God and before men.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27787S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27787S\"></sup>after several years I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27787T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27787T\"></sup>came to bring alms to my nation and to present offerings;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>in which they found me <i>occupied</i> in the temple, having been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27788U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27788U\"></sup>purified, without <i>any</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27788V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27788V\"></sup>crowd or uproar. But <i>there were</i> some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27788W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27788W\"></sup>Jews from Asia—",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>who ought to have been present before you and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27789X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27789X\"></sup>make accusation, if they should have anything against me.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Or else let these men themselves tell what misdeed they found when I stood before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27790Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27790Y\"></sup>the Council,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>other than for this one statement which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27791Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27791Z\"></sup>I shouted out while standing among them, ‘For the resurrection of the dead I am on trial before you today.’”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But Felix, having a more exact knowledge about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27792AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27792AA\"></sup>the Way, put them off, saying, “When Lysias the commander comes down, I will decide your case.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then he gave orders to the centurion for him to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27793AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27793AB\"></sup>kept in custody and <i>yet</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27793AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27793AC\"></sup>have <i>some</i> freedom, and not to prevent any of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27793AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27793AD\"></sup>his friends from ministering to him.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But some days later Felix arrived with Drusilla, his wife who was a Jewess, and sent for Paul and heard him <i>speak</i> about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27794AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27794AE\"></sup>faith in Christ Jesus.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But as he was discussing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27795AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27795AF\"></sup>righteousness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27795AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27795AG\"></sup>self-control and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27795AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27795AH\"></sup>the judgment to come, Felix became frightened and said, “Go away for the present, and when I find time I will summon you.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>At the same time too, he was hoping that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27796AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27796AI\"></sup>money would be given him by Paul; therefore he also used to send for him quite often and converse with him.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But after two years had passed, Felix was succeeded by Porcius <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27797AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27797AJ\"></sup>Festus, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27797AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27797AK\"></sup>wishing to do the Jews a favor, Felix left Paul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27797AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27797AL\"></sup>imprisoned."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>Festus then, having arrived in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27798A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27798A\"></sup>the province, three days later went up to Jerusalem from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27798B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27798B\"></sup>Caesarea.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the chief priests and the leading men of the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27799C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27799C\"></sup>brought charges against Paul, and they were urging him,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>requesting a concession against Paul, that he might have him brought to Jerusalem (<i>at the same time</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27800D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27800D\"></sup>setting an ambush to kill him on the way).",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Festus then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27801E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27801E\"></sup>answered that Paul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27801F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27801F\"></sup>was being kept in custody at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27801G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27801G\"></sup>Caesarea and that he himself was about to leave shortly.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Therefore,” he *said, “let the influential men among you go there with me, and if there is anything wrong about the man, let them prosecute him.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>After he had spent not more than eight or ten days among them, he went down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27803H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27803H\"></sup>Caesarea, and on the next day he took his seat on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27803I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27803I\"></sup>the tribunal and ordered Paul to be brought.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>After Paul arrived, the Jews who had come down from Jerusalem stood around him, bringing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27804J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27804J\"></sup>many and serious charges against him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27804K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27804K\"></sup>which they could not prove,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>while Paul said in his own defense, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27805L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27805L\"></sup>I have committed no offense either against the Law of the Jews or against the temple or against Caesar.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But Festus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27806M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27806M\"></sup>wishing to do the Jews a favor, answered Paul and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27806N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27806N\"></sup>Are you willing to go up to Jerusalem and stand trial before me on these <i>charges</i>?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But Paul said, “I am standing before Caesar’s <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27807O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27807O\"></sup>tribunal, where I ought to be tried. I have done no wrong to <i>the</i> Jews, as you also very well know.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If, then, I am a wrongdoer and have committed anything worthy of death, I do not refuse to die; but if none of those things is <i>true</i> of which these men accuse me, no one can hand me over to them. I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27808P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27808P\"></sup>appeal to Caesar.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then when Festus had conferred with his council, he answered, “You have appealed to Caesar, to Caesar you shall go.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now when several days had elapsed, King Agrippa and Bernice arrived at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27810Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27810Q\"></sup>Caesarea and paid their respects to Festus.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>While they were spending many days there, Festus laid Paul’s case before the king, saying, “There is a man who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27811R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27811R\"></sup>left as a prisoner by Felix;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and when I was at Jerusalem, the chief priests and the elders of the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27812S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27812S\"></sup>brought charges against him, asking for a sentence of condemnation against him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27813T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27813T\"></sup>answered them that it is not the custom of the Romans to hand over any man before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27813U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27813U\"></sup>the accused meets his accusers face to face and has an opportunity to make his defense against the charges.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So after they had assembled here, I did not delay, but on the next day took my seat on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27814V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27814V\"></sup>the tribunal and ordered the man to be brought before me.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When the accusers stood up, they <i>began</i> bringing charges against him not of such crimes as I was expecting,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>but they <i>simply</i> had some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27816W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27816W\"></sup>points of disagreement with him about their own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27816X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27816X\"></sup>religion and about a dead man, Jesus, whom Paul asserted to be alive.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27817Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27817Y\"></sup>Being at a loss how to investigate such matters, I asked whether he was willing to go to Jerusalem and there stand trial on these matters.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But when Paul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27818Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27818Z\"></sup>appealed to be held in custody for the Emperor’s decision, I ordered him to be kept in custody until I send him to Caesar.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27819AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27819AA\"></sup>Agrippa <i>said</i> to Festus, “I also would like to hear the man myself.” “Tomorrow,” he *said, “you shall hear him.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>So, on the next day when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27820AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27820AB\"></sup>Agrippa came together with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27820AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27820AC\"></sup>Bernice amid great pomp, and entered the auditorium accompanied by the commanders and the prominent men of the city, at the command of Festus, Paul was brought in.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Festus *said, “King Agrippa, and all you gentlemen here present with us, you see this man about whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27821AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27821AD\"></sup>all the people of the Jews appealed to me, both at Jerusalem and here, loudly declaring that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27821AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27821AE\"></sup>he ought not to live any longer.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But I found that he had committed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27822AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27822AF\"></sup>nothing worthy of death; and since he himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27822AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27822AG\"></sup>appealed to the Emperor, I decided to send him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Yet I have nothing definite about him to write to my lord. Therefore I have brought him before you <i>all</i> and especially before you, King Agrippa, so that after the investigation has taken place, I may have something to write.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For it seems absurd to me in sending a prisoner, not to indicate also the charges against him.”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27825A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27825A\"></sup>Agrippa said to Paul, “You are permitted to speak for yourself.” Then Paul stretched out his hand and <i>proceeded</i> to make his defense:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“In regard to all the things of which I am accused by the Jews, I consider myself fortunate, King Agrippa, that I am about to make my defense before you today;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>especially because you are an expert in all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27827B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27827B\"></sup>customs and questions among <i>the</i> Jews; therefore I beg you to listen to me patiently.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“So then, all Jews know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27828C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27828C\"></sup>my manner of life from my youth up, which from the beginning was spent among my <i>own</i> nation and at Jerusalem;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>since they have known about me for a long time, if they are willing to testify, that I lived <i>as</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27829D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27829D\"></sup>Pharisee <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27829E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27829E\"></sup>according to the strictest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27829F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27829F\"></sup>sect of our religion.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And now I am standing trial <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27830G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27830G\"></sup>for the hope of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27830H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27830H\"></sup>the promise made by God to our fathers;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><i>the promise</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27831I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27831I\"></sup>to which our twelve tribes hope to attain, as they earnestly serve <i>God</i> night and day. And for this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27831J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27831J\"></sup>hope, O King, I am being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27831K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27831K\"></sup>accused by Jews.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Why is it considered incredible among you <i>people</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27832L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27832L\"></sup>if God does raise the dead?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“So then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27833M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27833M\"></sup>I thought to myself that I had to do many things hostile to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27833N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27833N\"></sup>the name of Jesus of Nazareth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And this is just what I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27834O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27834O\"></sup>did in Jerusalem; not only did I lock up many of the saints in prisons, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27834P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27834P\"></sup>received authority from the chief priests, but also when they were being put to death I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27834Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27834Q\"></sup>cast my vote against them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27835R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27835R\"></sup>as I punished them often in all the synagogues, I tried to force them to blaspheme; and being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27835S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27835S\"></sup>furiously enraged at them, I kept pursuing them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27835T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27835T\"></sup>even to foreign cities.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“While so engaged <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27836U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27836U\"></sup>as I was journeying to Damascus with the authority and commission of the chief priests,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>at midday, O King, I saw on the way a light from heaven, brighter than the sun, shining all around me and those who were journeying with me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And when we had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27838V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27838V\"></sup>all fallen to the ground, I heard a voice saying to me in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27838W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27838W\"></sup>Hebrew dialect, <span class=\"woj\">‘Saul, Saul, why are you persecuting Me? It is hard for you to kick against the goads.’</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And I said, ‘Who are You, Lord?’ And the Lord said, <span class=\"woj\">‘I am Jesus whom you are persecuting.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But get up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27840X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27840X\"></sup>stand on your feet; for this purpose I have appeared to you, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27840Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27840Y\"></sup>appoint you a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27840Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27840Z\"></sup>minister and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27840AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27840AA\"></sup>a witness not only to the things which you have seen, but also to the things in which I will appear to you;</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27841AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27841AB\"></sup>rescuing you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27841AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27841AC\"></sup>from the <i>Jewish</i> people and from the Gentiles, to whom I am sending you,</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27842AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27842AD\"></sup>open their eyes so that they may turn from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27842AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27842AE\"></sup>darkness to light and from the dominion of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27842AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27842AF\"></sup>Satan to God, that they may receive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27842AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27842AG\"></sup>forgiveness of sins and an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27842AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27842AH\"></sup>inheritance among those who have been sanctified by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27842AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27842AI\"></sup>faith in Me.’</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“So, King Agrippa, I did not prove disobedient to the heavenly vision,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>but <i>kept</i> declaring both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27844AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27844AJ\"></sup>to those of Damascus first, and <i>also</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27844AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27844AK\"></sup>at Jerusalem and <i>then</i> throughout all the region of Judea, and <i>even</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27844AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27844AL\"></sup>to the Gentiles, that they should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27844AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27844AM\"></sup>repent and turn to God, performing deeds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27844AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27844AN\"></sup>appropriate to repentance.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For this reason <i>some</i> Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27845AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27845AO\"></sup>seized me in the temple and tried <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27845AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27845AP\"></sup>to put me to death.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So, having obtained help from God, I stand to this day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27846AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27846AQ\"></sup>testifying both to small and great, stating nothing but what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27846AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27846AR\"></sup>the Prophets and Moses said was going to take place;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27847AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27847AS\"></sup>that the Christ was to suffer, <i>and</i> that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27847AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27847AT\"></sup>by reason of <i>His</i> resurrection from the dead He would be the first to proclaim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27847AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27847AU\"></sup>light both to the <i>Jewish</i> people and to the Gentiles.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>While <i>Paul</i> was saying this in his defense, Festus *said in a loud voice, “Paul, you are out of your mind! <i>Your</i> great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27848AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27848AV\"></sup>learning is driving you mad.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But Paul *said, “I am not out of my mind, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27849AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27849AW\"></sup>most excellent Festus, but I utter words of sober truth.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For the king <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27850AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27850AX\"></sup>knows about these matters, and I speak to him also with confidence, since I am persuaded that none of these things escape his notice; for this has not been done in a corner.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>King Agrippa, do you believe the Prophets? I know that you do.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Agrippa <i>replied</i> to Paul, “In a short time you will persuade me to become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27852AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27852AY\"></sup>Christian.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And Paul <i>said</i>, “I would wish to God, that whether in a short or long time, not only you, but also all who hear me this day, might become such as I am, except for these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27853AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27853AZ\"></sup>chains.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27854BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27854BA\"></sup>The king stood up and the governor and Bernice, and those who were sitting with them,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>and when they had gone aside, they <i>began</i> talking to one another, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27855BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27855BB\"></sup>This man is not doing anything worthy of death or imprisonment.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And Agrippa said to Festus, “This man might have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27856BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27856BC\"></sup>set free if he had not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27856BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27856BD\"></sup>appealed to Caesar.”"
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>When it was decided that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27857A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27857A\"></sup>we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27857B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27857B\"></sup>would sail for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27857C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27857C\"></sup>Italy, they proceeded to deliver Paul and some other prisoners to a centurion of the Augustan <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27857D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27857D\"></sup>cohort named Julius.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And embarking in an Adramyttian ship, which was about to sail to the regions along the coast of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27858E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27858E\"></sup>Asia, we put out to sea accompanied by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27858F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27858F\"></sup>Aristarchus, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27858G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27858G\"></sup>Macedonian of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27858H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27858H\"></sup>Thessalonica.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The next day we put in at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27859I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27859I\"></sup>Sidon; and Julius <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27859J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27859J\"></sup>treated Paul with consideration and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27859K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27859K\"></sup>allowed him to go to his friends and receive care.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>From there we put out to sea and sailed under the shelter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27860L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27860L\"></sup>Cyprus because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27860M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27860M\"></sup>the winds were contrary.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When we had sailed through the sea along the coast of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27861N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27861N\"></sup>Cilicia and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27861O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27861O\"></sup>Pamphylia, we landed at Myra in Lycia.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>There the centurion found an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27862P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27862P\"></sup>Alexandrian ship sailing for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27862Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27862Q\"></sup>Italy, and he put us aboard it.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When we had sailed slowly for a good many days, and with difficulty had arrived off Cnidus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27863R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27863R\"></sup>since the wind did not permit us <i>to go</i> farther, we sailed under the shelter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27863S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27863S\"></sup>Crete, off Salmone;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and with difficulty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27864T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27864T\"></sup>sailing past it we came to a place called Fair Havens, near which was the city of Lasea.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When considerable time had passed and the voyage was now dangerous, since even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27865U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27865U\"></sup>the fast was already over, Paul <i>began</i> to admonish them,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and said to them, “Men, I perceive that the voyage will certainly be with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27866V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27866V\"></sup>damage and great loss, not only of the cargo and the ship, but also of our lives.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But the centurion was more persuaded by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27867W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27867W\"></sup>pilot and the captain of the ship than by what was being said by Paul.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Because the harbor was not suitable for wintering, the majority reached a decision to put out to sea from there, if somehow they could reach Phoenix, a harbor of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27868X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27868X\"></sup>Crete, facing southwest and northwest, and spend the winter <i>there</i>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When a moderate south wind came up, supposing that they had attained their purpose, they weighed anchor and <i>began</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27869Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27869Y\"></sup>sailing along <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27869Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27869Z\"></sup>Crete, close <i>inshore</i>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But before very long there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27870AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27870AA\"></sup>rushed down from the land a violent wind, called Euraquilo;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and when the ship was caught <i>in it</i> and could not face the wind, we gave way <i>to it</i> and let ourselves be driven along.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Running under the shelter of a small island called Clauda, we were scarcely able to get the <i>ship’s</i> boat under control.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>After they had hoisted it up, they used supporting cables in undergirding the ship; and fearing that they might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27873AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27873AB\"></sup>run aground on <i>the shallows</i> of Syrtis, they let down the sea anchor and in this way let themselves be driven along.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The next day as we were being violently storm-tossed, they began to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27874AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27874AC\"></sup>jettison the cargo;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and on the third day they threw the ship’s tackle overboard with their own hands.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Since neither sun nor stars appeared for many days, and no small storm was assailing <i>us</i>, from then on all hope of our being saved was gradually abandoned.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>When they had gone a long time without food, then Paul stood up in their midst and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27877AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27877AD\"></sup>Men, you ought to have followed my advice and not to have set sail from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27877AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27877AE\"></sup>Crete and incurred this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27877AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27877AF\"></sup>damage and loss.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><i>Yet</i> now I urge you to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27878AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27878AG\"></sup>keep up your courage, for there will be no loss of life among you, but <i>only</i> of the ship.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For this very night <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27879AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27879AH\"></sup>an angel of the God to whom I belong and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27879AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27879AI\"></sup>whom I serve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27879AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27879AJ\"></sup>stood before me,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>saying, ‘Do not be afraid, Paul; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27880AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27880AK\"></sup>you must stand before Caesar; and behold, God has granted you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27880AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27880AL\"></sup>all those who are sailing with you.’",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27881AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27881AM\"></sup>keep up your courage, men, for I believe God that it will turn out exactly as I have been told.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But we must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27882AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27882AN\"></sup>run aground on a certain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27882AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27882AO\"></sup>island.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But when the fourteenth night came, as we were being driven about in the Adriatic Sea, about midnight the sailors <i>began</i> to surmise that they were approaching some land.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>They took soundings and found <i>it to be</i> twenty fathoms; and a little farther on they took another sounding and found <i>it to be</i> fifteen fathoms.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Fearing that we might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27885AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27885AP\"></sup>run aground somewhere on the rocks, they cast four anchors from the stern and wished for daybreak.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But as the sailors were trying to escape from the ship and had let down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27886AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27886AQ\"></sup>the <i>ship’s</i> boat into the sea, on the pretense of intending to lay out anchors from the bow,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Paul said to the centurion and to the soldiers, “Unless these men remain in the ship, you yourselves cannot be saved.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Then the soldiers cut away the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27888AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27888AR\"></sup>ropes of the <i>ship’s</i> boat and let it fall away.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Until the day was about to dawn, Paul was encouraging them all to take some food, saying, “Today is the fourteenth day that you have been constantly watching and going without eating, having taken nothing.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Therefore I encourage you to take some food, for this is for your preservation, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27890AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27890AS\"></sup>not a hair from the head of any of you will perish.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Having said this, he took bread and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27891AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27891AT\"></sup>gave thanks to God in the presence of all, and he broke it and began to eat.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>All <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27892AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27892AU\"></sup>of them were encouraged and they themselves also took food.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>All of us in the ship were two hundred and seventy-six <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27893AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27893AV\"></sup>persons.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>When they had eaten enough, they <i>began</i> to lighten the ship by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27894AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27894AW\"></sup>throwing out the wheat into the sea.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>When day came, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27895AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27895AX\"></sup>they could not recognize the land; but they did observe a bay with a beach, and they resolved to drive the ship onto it if they could.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And casting off <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27896AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27896AY\"></sup>the anchors, they left them in the sea while at the same time they were loosening the ropes of the rudders; and hoisting the foresail to the wind, they were heading for the beach.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>But striking a reef where two seas met, they ran the vessel aground; and the prow stuck fast and remained immovable, but the stern <i>began</i> to be broken up by the force <i>of the waves</i>.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>The soldiers’ plan was to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27898AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27898AZ\"></sup>kill the prisoners, so that none <i>of them</i> would swim away and escape;",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>but the centurion, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27899BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27899BA\"></sup>wanting to bring Paul safely through, kept them from their intention, and commanded that those who could swim should jump overboard first and get to land,",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>and the rest <i>should follow</i>, some on planks, and others on various things from the ship. And so it happened that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27900BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27900BB\"></sup>they all were brought safely to land."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27901A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27901A\"></sup>they had been brought safely through, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27901B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27901B\"></sup>then we found out that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27901C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27901C\"></sup>the island was called Malta.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27902D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27902D\"></sup>The natives showed us extraordinary kindness; for because of the rain that had set in and because of the cold, they kindled a fire and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27902E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27902E\"></sup>received us all.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But when Paul had gathered a bundle of sticks and laid them on the fire, a viper came out because of the heat and fastened itself on his hand.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27904F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27904F\"></sup>the natives saw the creature hanging from his hand, they <i>began</i> saying to one another, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27904G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27904G\"></sup>Undoubtedly this man is a murderer, and though he has been saved from the sea, justice has not allowed him to live.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>However <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27905H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27905H\"></sup>he shook the creature off into the fire and suffered no harm.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But they were expecting that he was about to swell up or suddenly fall down dead. But after they had waited a long time and had seen nothing unusual happen to him, they changed their minds and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27906I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27906I\"></sup><i>began</i> to say that he was a god.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now in the neighborhood of that place were lands belonging to the leading man of the island, named Publius, who welcomed us and entertained us courteously three days.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And it happened that the father of Publius was lying <i>in bed</i> afflicted with <i>recurrent</i> fever and dysentery; and Paul went in <i>to see</i> him and after he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27908J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27908J\"></sup>prayed, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27908K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27908K\"></sup>laid his hands on him and healed him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>After this had happened, the rest of the people on the island who had diseases were coming to him and getting cured.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They also honored us with many marks of respect; and when we were setting sail, they supplied <i>us</i> with all we needed.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>At the end of three months we set sail on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27911L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27911L\"></sup>an Alexandrian ship which had wintered at the island, and which had the Twin Brothers for its figurehead.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>After we put in at Syracuse, we stayed there for three days.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>From there we sailed around and arrived at Rhegium, and a day later a south wind sprang up, and on the second day we came to Puteoli.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>There we found <i>some</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27914M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27914M\"></sup>brethren, and were invited to stay with them for seven days; and thus we came to Rome.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27915N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27915N\"></sup>brethren, when they heard about us, came from there as far as the Market of Appius and Three Inns to meet us; and when Paul saw them, he thanked God and took courage.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When we entered Rome, Paul was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27916O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27916O\"></sup>allowed to stay by himself, with the soldier who was guarding him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>After three days Paul called together those who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27917P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27917P\"></sup>the leading men of the Jews, and when they came together, he <i>began</i> saying to them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27917Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27917Q\"></sup>Brethren, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27917R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27917R\"></sup>though I had done nothing against our people or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27917S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27917S\"></sup>the customs of our fathers, yet I was delivered as a prisoner from Jerusalem into the hands of the Romans.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And when they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27918T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27918T\"></sup>examined me, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27918U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27918U\"></sup>were willing to release me because there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27918V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27918V\"></sup>no ground for putting me to death.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But when the Jews objected, I was forced to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27919W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27919W\"></sup>appeal to Caesar, not that I had any accusation against my nation.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For this reason, therefore, I requested to see you and to speak with you, for I am wearing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27920X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27920X\"></sup>this chain for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27920Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27920Y\"></sup>the sake of the hope of Israel.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They said to him, “We have neither received letters from Judea concerning you, nor have any of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27921Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27921Z\"></sup>the brethren come here and reported or spoken anything bad about you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But we desire to hear from you what your views are; for concerning this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27922AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27922AA\"></sup>sect, it is known to us that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27922AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27922AB\"></sup>it is spoken against everywhere.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When they had set a day for Paul, they came to him at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27923AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27923AC\"></sup>his lodging in large numbers; and he was explaining to them by solemnly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27923AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27923AD\"></sup>testifying about the kingdom of God and trying to persuade them concerning Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27923AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27923AE\"></sup>from both the Law of Moses and from the Prophets, from morning until evening.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27924AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27924AF\"></sup>Some were being persuaded by the things spoken, but others would not believe.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And when they did not agree with one another, they <i>began</i> leaving after Paul had spoken one <i>parting</i> word, “The Holy Spirit rightly spoke through Isaiah the prophet to your fathers,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>saying,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27926AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27926AG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Go to this people and say</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27926AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27926AH\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You will keep on hearing</span>, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">but will not understand</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">you will keep on seeing, but will not perceive</span>;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27927AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27927AI\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For the heart of this people has become dull</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And with their ears they scarcely hear</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And they have closed their eyes</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Otherwise they might see with their eyes</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And hear with their ears</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And understand with their heart and return</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And I would heal them</span>.”’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore let it be known to you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27928AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27928AJ\"></sup>this salvation of God has been sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27928AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27928AK\"></sup>to the Gentiles; they will also listen.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>[When he had spoken these words, the Jews departed, having a great dispute among themselves.]",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And he stayed two full years in his own rented quarters and was welcoming all who came to him,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27931AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27931AL\"></sup>preaching the kingdom of God and teaching concerning the Lord Jesus Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-27931AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-27931AM\"></sup>with all openness, unhindered."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;